do-Bangladesh%20border%20where%20prohibitory%20orders%20have%20been%20imposed%20on%20all%20entry%20points%2C%20on%20Wednesday.%20While%20some%20women%20who%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20Trinamool%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan's%20aides%20agreed%20to%20speak%2C%20none%20of%20them%20wanted%20to%20reveal%20their%20identity%20in%20front%20of%20television%20cameras%2C%20fearing%20reprisal%20and%20persecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%2C%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20protests%20earlier%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20incidents%20must%20have%20taken%20place%2C%20otherwise%20why%20will%20the%20women%20say%20these%20things%3F%20You%20must%20enquire%20for%20yourself.%20Why%20else%20will%20women%20come%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20speak%20out%3F%20Are%20they%20lying%3F%20There%20must%20be%20truth%20in%20these%20statements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20living%20in%20fear.%20We%20don't%20come%20out%20of%20our%20homes%20because%20of%20fear%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20woman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(Shahjahan's%20aides)%20would%20call%20women%20for%20meetings%20or%20rallies%20but%20there%20was%20no%20fixed%20time.%20It%20could%20be%20day%20or%20night.%20We%20would%20have%20to%20go%20whenever%20they%20called%20and%20if%20we%20didn't%2C%20they%20would%20threaten%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20did%20not%20want%20to%20go%2C%20they%20would%20force%20us.%20They%20gave%20us%20examples%20of%20the%20Lakshmi%20Bhandar%20scheme%20and%20the%20free%20rice%20scheme.%20They%20said%20Didi%20(West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee)%20is%20feeding%20you%20but%20you%20still%20won't%20go%20to%20meetings%3F%20Even%20if%20it%20is%20at%20night%2C%20you%20have%20to%20go%20or%20we%20will%20kidnap%20you%2C%20they%20would%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20woman%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20named%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan's%20aides%2C%20Shibu%20Hazra%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar.%20While%20Sardar%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20Hazra%20is%20on%20the%20run.%20Shahjahan%20has%20also%20been%20missing%20since%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20team%20was%20attacked%20by%20a%20mob%20during%20a%20raid%20on%20his%20house%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20ration%20scam%20on%20January%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShibu%20Hazra%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar%20would%20call%20us%20to%20the%20party%20office%20even%20at%20night%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20holding%20a%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20woman%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20there%20have%20been%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20the%20woman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20would%20torture%20us.%20They%20targeted%20women%20by%20picking%20up%20their%20husbands%20and%20beating%20them%20up%20with%20a%20stick%20in%20the%20party%20office.%20If%20we%20refused%20to%20go%20to%20the%20party%20office%2C%20they%20would%20pick%20up%20the%20men%20and%20thrash%20them%20so%20we%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClaims%2C%20Counterclaims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20West%20Bengal%20BJP%20President%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20allegedly%20suffered%20injuries%20during%20a%20clash%20with%20the%20police%20as%20he%20attempted%20to%20go%20to%20Sandeshkhali%20despite%20police%20restrictions%20and%20prohibitory%20orders.%20He%20has%20been%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Kolkata.%20Some%20have%20claimed%20Mr%20Majumdar's%20injuries%20were%20the%20result%20of%20him%20falling%20after%20climbing%20atop%20a%20police%20car%20to%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20women%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20and%20raped%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20wanted%20to%20visit%20the%20area%20to%20speak%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Legislative%20Assembly%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari.%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%