r%20for%20Germany%2C%20for%20whom%20China%20is%20the%20biggest%20market%20for%20carmakers%20including%20Volkswagen%20AG.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20sanctions%20need%20the%20backing%20of%20all%20member%20states%20to%20be%20adopted%20and%20could%20change%20before%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20from%20the%20commission%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20proposal.%20A%20message%20left%20with%20China's%20embassy%20in%20Brussels%20wasn't%20immediately%20returned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mostly%20technology%20and%20electronics%20companies%20are%20accused%20of%20%26quot%3Bcontributing%20to%20Russia's%20military%20and%20technological%20enhancement%20or%20to%20the%20development%20of%20Russia's%20defense%20and%20security%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommission%20President%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20traveled%20to%20Beijing%20in%20April%20and%20warned%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20against%20getting%20involved%20in%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEurope's%20Record%20Trade%20Deficit%20With%20China%20Has%20Come%20Down%20%C2%A0%7C%20But%20is%20still%20much%20higher%20than%20pre-pandemic%20levels%20as%20Chinese%20exports%20soared%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20also%20count%20on%20China%20not%20to%20provide%20any%20military%20equipment%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly%2C%20to%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20von%20der%20Leyen%20said%20in%20Beijing.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20we%20all%20know%2C%20arming%20the%20aggressor%20would%20be%20against%20international%20law.%20And%20it%20would%20significantly%20harm%20our%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposals%20include%20three%20Chinese%20firms%20and%20one%20each%20from%20India%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Serbia%2C%20Kazakhstan%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Turkey%20and%20Hong%20Kong.%20Their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20proposed%20list%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20entail%20any%20attribution%20of%20responsibility%20for%20their%20actions%20to%20the%20jurisdiction%20in%20which%20they%20are%20operating%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20says.%20The%20EU%20has%20so%20far%20listed%20more%20than%20620%20companies%2C%20with%20the%20near%20entirety%20from%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20are%20mostly%20importing%20banned%20technologies%20and%20electronics%20and%20reexporting%20the%20goods%20to%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20a%20package%20of%20sanctions%20to%20mark%20two%20years%20since%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20EU%20has%20also%20proposed%20sanctions%20on%20more%20than%20110%20people%20and%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707962580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-06%2Feuropean-union_650x400_61497367967.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feuropean-union-proposes-curbs-on-indian-chinese-firms-for-aiding-russia-report-5060370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20European%20Union%20has%20proposed%20new%20trade%20restrictions%20on%20about%20two%20dozen%20firms%2C%20including%20three%20based%20in%20China%2C%20accused%20of%20supporting%20Russia's%20war%20efforts%20in%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feuropean-union-proposes-curbs-on-indian-chinese-firms-for-aiding-russia-report-5060370%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feuropean-union-proposes-curbs-on-indian-chinese-firms-for-aiding-russia-report-5060370%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feuropean-union-proposes-curbs-on-indian-chinese-firms-for-aiding-russia-report-5060370%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indonesia%20Elections%3A%20Jokowi%20Leaves%2C%20But%20Lives%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15003633%2FJoko-W.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C2024%20is%20not%20just%20an%20election%20year.%20It%E2%80%99s%20perhaps%20the%20election%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6550920%2Fworld-elections-2024%2F%5C%22%3Eread%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3ETime%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine.%20At%20least%2064%20countries%20across%20the%20globe%20are%20scheduled%20to%20witness%20national%20elections.%20Of%20these%2064%2C%20the%20fourth-most%20populous%20and%20the%20third-largest%20democratic%20country%20%E2%80%93%20Indonesia%20%E2%80%93%20elected%20a%20new%20president%20and%20vice%20president%20along%20with%20parliamentary%20and%20local%20representatives%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F02%2F13%2Fasia%2Findonesia-general-election-explainer-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Elargest%3C%2Fa%3E%20single-day%20election%20on%20February%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unofficial%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fasia%2Fse-asia%2Findonesia-elections-vote-counting-begins-as-polls-close%5C%22%3Eearly%20results%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20quick%20count%20tallies%20from%20independent%20survey%20agencies%20indicate%20a%20victory%20for%20Prabowo%20Subianto%20and%20Gibran%20Rakabuming%20Raka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20official%20results%20will%20not%20be%20known%20until%20March%2C%20they%20are%20not%20expected%20to%20differ%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20election%2C%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20seventh%2C%20is%20particularly%20important%20as%20it%20witnesses%20a%20change%20of%20guard%20as%20President%20Joko%20Widodo%20concludes%20his%20second%20and%20constitutionally%20final%20term%20in%20office.%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EIstana%20Merdeka%3C%2Fem%3E%20(its%20official%20residence)%20will%20have%20a%20new%20occupant%20soon.%20While%20succession%20is%20a%20certainty%20in%20Indonesia%2C%20there%20are%20questions%20as%20to%20its%20relative%20or%20absolute%20nature.%20At%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20conundrum%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penguin.sg%2Fbook%2Fman-of-contradictions%2F%5C%22%3EMan%20of%20Contradictions%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Joko%20Widodo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20draft%20will%20outline%20Widodo%E2%80%99s%20impact%20on%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20political%20landscape%20and%20how%20he%20seeks%20to%20maintain%20an%20influence%20in%20Jakarta%20even%20after%20he%20steps%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22200%20Million%20Voters%20and%20820%2C000%20Polling%20Stations%3A%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20Massive%20Election%20in%C2%A0Numbers%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2F200-million-voters-and-820000-polling-stations-indonesias-massive-election-in-numbers%5C%22%3E200%20Million%20Voters%20and%20820%2C000%20Polling%20Stations%3A%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20Massive%20Election%20in%C2%A0Numbers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20raison%20d%E2%80%99etre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoko%20Widodo%2C%20or%20Jokowi%20as%20he%20is%20popularly%20known%2C%20is%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20fifth%20president%20since%20the%20initiation%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20political%20reformation%2C%20Reformasi%2C%20in%201998.%20He%20is%20also%20only%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20third%20democratically%20elected%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20rank%20outsider%2C%20Jokowi%20was%20a%20furniture%20maker%20in%20Solo%20with%20no%20linkages%20to%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20political%20and%20military%20elite.%20His%20rise%20to%20power%20captured%20the%20imagination%20and%20aspirations%20of%20the%20average%20Indonesian.%20Even%20today%2C%20as%20Jokowi%20prepares%20to%20leave%20office%2C%20he%20enjoys%20a%2076%25%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjakartaglobe.id%2Fnews%2Fjokowis-approval-rating-hits-76-in-lsi-survey%5C%22%3Eapproval%20rating%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202005%2C%20Jokowi%20won%20a%20mayoral%20seat%20in%20Surakarta%20and%20in%202012%20the%20governorship%20of%20Jakarta.%20He%20then%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20as%20president%20challenged%20the%20dominant%20political%20powers%20in%20Jakarta.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F322c7f9b-310a-4c4f-ae6e-598328f59028%5C%22%3EAccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20journalist%20Ben%20Bland%2C%20this%20once-furniture%20maker%20campaigned%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccountry%20with%20faster%20economic%20growth%2C%20lower%20rates%20of%20poverty%2C%20more%20jobs%2C%20less%20corruption%20and%20a%20political%20system%20that%20served%20the%20people%2C%20not%20the%20powerful%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%20focused%20Indonesia%20on%20economic%20development%20and%20corruption-free%20leadership.%20In%20his%202019%20inauguration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thejakartapost.com%2Fnews%2F2019%2F10%2F20%2Fthe-main-thing-is-not-the-process-but-the-result-jokowis-full-inauguration-speech.html%5C%22%3Espeech%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20laid%20out%20his%20ambition%20to%20make%20Indonesia%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202045%20and%20one%20of%20the%20top%20five%20world%20economies%20with%20a%20poverty%20rate%20nearing%200%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20we%20look%20at%20the%20five%20key%20pillars%20of%20this%20plan%20%E2%80%93%20economic%20growth%2C%20poverty%20eradication%2C%20anti-corruption%2C%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20and%20infrastructure%20development%20%E2%80%93%20we%20learn%20that%20not%20much%20has%20changed%20in%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20bid%20to%20reform%20the%20political%20system%20has%20also%20fallen%20by%20the%20wayside.%20The%20system%20that%20serves%20the%20people%20now%20also%20serves%20the%20powerful%20more.%20They%20consist%20of%20the%20forces%20of%20conservative%20Islam%2C%20the%20party%20oligarchs%2C%20the%20military%20and%20Jokowi%20himself.%20Over%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20Jokowi%20has%20done%20much%20to%20entrench%20himself%20in%20Indonesian%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20scoreboard%20remains%20moderate.%20As%20of%202024%2C%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20economy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbesindia.com%2Farticle%2Fexplainers%2Ftop-10-largest-economies-in-the-world%2F86159%2F1%5C%22%3Eremains%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20sixteenth%20position%2C%20the%20same%20as%20in%202019.%20This%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20other%20economic%20parameters.%20According%20to%20the%20World%20Bank%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.worldbank.org%2Findicator%2FSI.POV.NAHC%3Flocations%3DID%26most_recent_year_desc%3Dtrue%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20country%20has%20made%20a%20fair%20bit%20of%20progress%20under%20Jokowi%20in%20bringing%20down%20the%20poverty%20rate%20%E2%80%93%20from%20approximately%2011.3%25%20to%209.5%25%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findonesia-elections-what-you-need-to-know%5C%22%3EIndonesia%20Elections%3A%20What%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20numbers%20have%20more%20or%20less%20remained%20static%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20second%20Jokowi%20administration%20%E2%80%93%209.4%25%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20of%20static%20numbers%20is%20mirrored%20in%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20corruption%20perception%20index%20(CPI)%20as%20well.%20Data%20from%20Transparency%20International%20shows%20that%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%202023%20CPI%20score%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transparency.org%2Fen%2Fcpi%2F2023%2Findex%2Fidn%5C%22%3Esimilar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%202014%20score%3A%2034%2F100.%20While%20the%20score%20remains%20the%20same%2C%20its%20ranking%20out%20of%20180%20countries%20has%20fallen%20from%20107%20to%20115%2C%20except%20for%20in%202019%20when%20it%20ranked%2085th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unemployment%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceicdata.com%2Fen%2Findicator%2Findonesia%2Funemployment-rate%5C%22%3Erate%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20ranged%20between%205%25%20to%206%25%20from%202014%20to%202023%2C%20except%20for%20a%20rise%20to%207%25%20in%202020%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20all%20the%20parameters%2C%20Indonesia%20under%20Jokowi%20has%20done%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.doingbusiness.org%2Fen%2Fdata%2Fexploreeconomies%2Findonesia%5C%22%3Ebest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20ease%20of%20doing%20business.%20From%20a%20rank%20of%20120%20in%202014%2C%20Indonesia%20rose%20to%2073rd%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%20had%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F322c7f9b-310a-4c4f-ae6e-598328f59028%5C%22%3Epositioned%3C%2Fa%3E%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cking%20of%20infrastructure%E2%80%9D.%20During%20his%20tenure%2C%20progress%20on%20several%20big-ticket%20infrastructure%20projects%20such%20as%20the%20Trans-Sumatra%20toll%20road%2C%20the%20Pemalang-Batang%20Toll%20Road%20in%20central%20Java%2C%20the%20Jatigede%20Dam%20in%20west%20Java%20and%20the%20Jakarta%20Mass%20Rapid%20Transit%20(MRT)%20amongst%20others%20have%20allowed%20him%20to%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20numbers%20project%20an%20above-average%20outcome%2C%20they%20have%20been%20enough%20to%20keep%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20political%20manoeuvres%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20the%20political%20arena%20though%2C%20that%20we%20see%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20serious%20successes.%20These%20include%20constitutional%20amendments%2C%20electoral%20manipulations%20and%20political%20manoeuvres%20allowing%20him%20to%20secure%20a%20powerful%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202014%20presidential%20elections%2C%20Jokowi%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fspectre-of-anti-communist-smears-resurrected-against-jokowi-28730%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20being%20from%20a%20secret%20Christian%20Chinese%20community%20with%20communist%20sympathies.%20Given%20the%20historical%20tensions%20between%20the%20Indonesian%20Islamists%20and%20communists%2C%20these%20accusations%20dented%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20ambition.%20This%20motivated%20Jokowi%20to%20co-opt%20Islamic%20hardliner%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20very%20near%20end%20of%20his%20campaign%2C%20Jokowi%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fas-indonesia-vote-nears-a-trip-to-mecca-1404746650%5C%22%3Emade%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20trip%20to%20Mecca.%20Two%20years%20into%20his%20presidency%20in%202016%2C%20Jokowi%20aligned%20himself%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98212%E2%80%99%20movement%20led%20by%20religious%20extremists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjakartaglobe.id%2Fnews%2Funderstanding-212-movement%5C%22%3Eagainst%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20then-governor%20of%20Jakarta%20and%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20close%20ally%2C%20Basuki%20Tjahaja%20Purnama%20(Ahok).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20revolved%20around%20the%20alleged%20blasphemy%20against%20Islam%20by%20Jakarta%E2%80%99s%20Christian%20Chinese%20governor%20Ahok.%20The%20protestors%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmandala.org%2Fjokowi-hands-strategic-victory-radicals%2F%5C%22%3Evalidated%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20presence%20on%20stage%20alongside%20the%20extremist%20leaders.%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20concern%20was%20so%20strong%20that%20he%20not%20only%20allowed%20his%20one-time%20ally%20Ahok%20to%20be%20thrown%20under%20the%20bus%2C%20but%20he%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticles%2F2018-08-09%2Findonesia-s-jokowi-picks-muslim-cleric-in-bid-for-second-term%5C%22%3Epartnered%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Ma%E2%80%99ruf%20Amin%2C%20the%20ex-head%20of%20Nahdlatul%20Ulama%2C%20who%20became%20his%20vice-presidential%20candidate%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20push%20for%20the%20military%20to%20re-enter%20Indonesian%20politics%20and%20business%20has%20also%20turned%20the%20political%20tables%20in%20Jakarta.%20Their%20re-entry%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Farticles%2Fgenerals-gaining-ground-civil-military-relations-and-democracy-in-indonesia%2F%5C%22%3Eignited%3C%2Fa%3E%20conversations%20on%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20Suharto-era%20doctrine%20of%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Edwi%20fungsi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(or%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdual%20function%E2%80%9D)%20which%20ended%20in%201998.%C2%A0%20Under%20Jokowi%2C%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20dual%20role%20became%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thejakartapost.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F09%2F20%2Findonesian-military-deployed-for-coronavirus-fight.html%5C%22%3Eapparent%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20the%20military%20was%20deployed%20to%20enforce%20health%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20has%20also%20witnessed%20the%20appointment%20of%20military%20officials%20to%20political%20committees%20and%20their%20inclusion%20in%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20inner%20circle.%20Some%20powerful%20military%20appointees%20include%20minister%20of%20maritime%20affairs%20and%20investments%20Luhut%20Pandjaitan%2C%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20chief%20of%20staff%20Moeldoko%20and%20defence%20minister%20Prabowo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabowo%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2019%2F10%2F23%2Findonesias-widodo-appoints-archrival-as-defence-minister%5C%22%3Einclusion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20is%20the%20most%20intriguing%20of%20them%20all.%20Peace%20with%20Prabowo%2C%20dictator%20Suharto%E2%80%99s%20son-in-law%20and%20a%20general%20with%20countless%20human%20rights%20abuses%20to%20his%20name%2C%20serves%20as%20a%20glaring%20example%20of%20the%20power%20infused%20into%20Islamists%2C%20party%20oligarchs%20and%20the%20military%20by%20Jokowi.%20It%20is%20this%20nexus%20that%20provides%20Jokowi%20continued%20influence%20in%20Jakarta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14214333%2FPrabowo-III-1024x512.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14214333%2FPrabowo-III-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14214333%2FPrabowo-III-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14214333%2FPrabowo-III-800x400.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14214333%2FPrabowo-III.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697186%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrabowo%20has%20claimed%20the%20presidential%20elections%20with%20a%20commanding%2058%25%20of%20the%20vote.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40Gerindra.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabowo%2C%20the%20incumbent%20defence%20minister%20and%20now%20the%20president-elect%2C%20has%20been%20a%20president-in-waiting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-probables-of-indonesia-presidential-elections-2024-7876723.html%5C%22%3Esince%3C%2Fa%3E%202004.%20He%20was%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20opponent%20in%202014%20and%202019.%20After%20realising%20that%20a%20smear%20campaign%20against%20Jokowi%20was%20insufficient%2C%20Prabowo%20aligned%20with%20the%20same%20hardline%20forces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthegeopolitics.com%2Funderstanding-jokowis-return-to-power-in-indonesia%2F%5C%22%3Eassociated%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20212%20movement%20to%20oppose%20Jokowi%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabowo%20was%20dismissed%20from%20his%20military%20duties%20after%20the%201998%20Indonesian%20riots%20and%20was%20denied%20a%20US%20visa%20for%20almost%2020%20years.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20succeeded%20in%20perhaps%20his%20last%20attempt%20at%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20alongside%20Prabowo%20as%20the%20vice%20president-elect%20is%20none%20other%20than%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20eldest%20son%2C%20Gibran%20Rakabuming%20Raka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaka%2C%2036%2C%20is%20the%20incumbent%20mayor%20of%20Surakarta%2C%20a%20seat%20that%20his%20father%20once%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20not%2C%20however%2C%20eligible%20to%20run%20for%20these%20elections%20owing%20to%20the%20minimum%20age%20criteria%20of%2040%20years.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbcindonesia.com%2Fresearch%2F20231017064610-128-481086%2Fputusan-mk-gibran-12-kepala-daerah-ini-bisa-maju-cawapres%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Constitutional%20Court%20of%20Indonesia%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20brother-in-law%20Anwar%20Usman%20allowed%20%E2%80%9Csomeone%20who%20is%20not%20yet%2040%20years%20old%20to%20run%20for%20president%20or%20vice%20president%20as%20long%20as%20they%20have%20experience%20as%20a%20regional%20head%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20to%20a%20major%20uproar%20across%20Indonesia%2C%20but%20helped%20secure%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Jokowi%20leaves%20behind%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20transformation%20from%20a%20rank%20outsider%20to%20a%20consummate%20insider%20has%20reached%20its%20final%20lap.%20His%20original%20raison%20d%E2%80%99%C3%AAtre%20started%20to%20peel%20away%20as%20he%20built%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Findonesias-new-cabinet-built-on-political-transactions-63196%5C%22%3Ebig%20tent%20coalition%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C