lso%20seen%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20deepening%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20inaugurating%20the%20temple%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20golden%20chapter%20in%20human%20history%20has%20been%20written%20in%20UAE%20today.%20A%20grand%20and%20holy%20temple%20has%20been%20inaugurated%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20today.%20Years%20of%20hard%20work%20have%20gone%20into%20this%20temple%20and%20a%20long-cherished%20dream%20has%20come%20true.%20Bhagwan%20Swaminarayan's%20blessings%20are%20also%20with%20this%20temple.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20amid%20cheers%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20centuries-old%20dream%20was%20fulfilled.%20All%20of%20India%20and%20every%20Indian%20is%20still%20cherishing%20that%20feeling.%20My%20friend%20Brahmavihari%20Swamy%20was%20saying%2C%20'Modi%20ji%20is%20the%20biggest%20priest'.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20have%20the%20qualifications%20of%20a%20temple%20priest%20but%20I%20am%20proud%20to%20be%20a%20priest%20of%20Maa%20Bharti%20(Mother%20India).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20every%20moment%20of%20his%20life%20and%20every%20molecule%20in%20his%20body%20is%20dedicated%20to%20Ma%20Bharti%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20joy%20we%20felt%20in%20Ayodhya%20has%20been%20amplified%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20today.%20It%20is%20my%20honour%20that%20I%20witnessed%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20last%20month%20and%20this%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Even%20Thank%20You%20Not%20Enough'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20his%20praise%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Bbrother%26quot%3B%2C%20UAE%20President%20Sheikh%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20hailed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfriend%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20'Ahlan%20Modi'%20event%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20he%20had%20played%20the%20biggest%20role%20in%20fulfilling%20the%20dream%20of%20constructing%20a%20grand%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20won%20the%20hearts%20of%20140%20crore%20Indians.%20It%20is%20my%20privilege%20that%20I%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20this%20temple%20from%20the%20time%20it%20was%20conceptualised%20to%20its%20inauguration.%20This%20is%20why%20I%20know%20that%20even%20'thank%20you'%20is%20too%20small%20a%20phrase%20for%20his%20generosity%20and%20contribution.%20I%20want%20the%20world%20to%20see%20the%20depth%20of%20the%20India-UAE%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20Sheikh%20Al%20Nahyan%20about%20the%20temple%20when%20they%20had%20met%20in%202015%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20the%20UAE%20president%20had%20said%20yes%20to%20the%20proposal%20on%20the%20spot%20and%20made%20land%20available%20in%20a%20short%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20came%20to%20the%20UAE%20again%20in%202018%2C%20I%20met%20Sheikh%20Al%20Nahyan%20and%20showed%20him%20the%20two%20models%20of%20the%20temple%20that%20had%20been%20prepared%20-%20one%20that%20was%20based%20on%20Vedic%20architecture%20and%20another%20that%20was%20a%20simple%20model%20without%20Hindu%20religious%20symbols%20-%20his%20thought%20was%20clear%3A%20he%20told%20me%20the%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20should%20be%20built%20with%20splendour%20and%20glory.%20He%20wanted%20the%20temple%20to%20not%20only%20be%20built%20but%20also%20look%20like%20a%20temple%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20and%20then%20asked%20the%20audience%20to%20give%20the%20UAE%20President%20a%20standing%20ovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstruction%20Began%20In%202019%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Al%20Nahyan%20donated%2013.5%20acres%20of%20land%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20in%202015%20and%20PM%20Modi%20had%20laid%20the%20foundation%20three%20years%20later.%20Construction%20began%20in%202019%20after%20an%20additional%2013.5%20acres%20of%20land%20was%20donated%20earlier%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20by%20the%20Bochasanwasi%20Shri%20Akshar%20Purushottam%20Swaminarayan%20Sanstha%20(BAPS)%2C%20the%20temple%20is%20located%20in%20Abu%20Mreikhah%2C%20near%20Al%20Rahba.%20The%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20idols%20began%20at%20the%20temple%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20participated%20in%20a%20'global%20aarti%20(prayer)'%2C%20which%20was%20performed%20simultaneously%20at%20over%201%2C200%20temples%20built%20by%20BAPS.%20Before%20inaugurating%20the%20temple%2C%20he%20offered%20water%20in%20the%20virtual%20Ganga%20and%20Yamuna%20rivers%20at%20the%20temple%20and%20met%20people%20from%20different%20religions%20who%20played%20a%20role%20in%20its%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpires%20Represent%20Emirates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemple%20authorities%20said%20seven%20%3Cem%3Eshikhars%3C%2Fem%3E%20(spires)%20have%20been%20built%20at%20the%20temple%20representing%20the%20seven%20emirates%20that%20form%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20seven%20spires%20have%20idols%20of%20deities%2C%20including%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20Lord%20Shiv%2C%20Lord%20Jagannath%2C%20Lord%20Krishna%2C%20Lord%20Swaminarayan%20(considered%20a%20reincarnation%20of%20Lord%20Krishna)%2C%20Tirupati%20Balaji%20and%20Lord%20Ayappa.%20The%20seven%20shikhars%20represent%20the%20seven%20emirates%20of%20UAE%2C%26quot%3B%20Swami%20Brahmaviharidas%2C%20head%20of%20international%20relations%20for%20BAPS%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20seven%20spires%20also%20pay%20homage%20to%20seven%20important%20deities%2C%20underscoring%20the%20interconnectedness%20of%20cultures%20and%20religions.%20Normally%2C%20our%20temples%20are%20either%20one%20spire%2C%20three%2C%20or%20five%20but%20the%20seven%20spires%20express%20our%20gratitude%20to%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20seven%20emirates.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20seven%20spires%20enshrine%20seven%20important%20deities...%20The%20spirals%20aim%20to%20promote%20unity%20and%20harmony%20in%20the%20multicultural%20landscape%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20UAE%20is%20his%20seventh%20since%202015%20and%20his%20third%20in%20eight%20months.%20After%20the%20temple%20inauguration%2C%20PM%20Modi%20left%20for%20Doha%2C%20where%20he%20will%20hold%20discussions%20with%20the%20Qatari%20leadership.%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20country%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Qatar%20releasing%20eight%20navy%20veterans%20from%20prison%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20huge%20diplomatic%20victory%20for%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707961500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fb7imqef_pm-modi-inaugurates-baps-temple-in-abu-dhabi_625x300_14_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-set-to-inaugurate-first-hindu-temple-in-abu-dhabi-5056901%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Marking%20a%20significant%20milestone%20for%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20inaugurating%20Abu%20Dhabi's%20first%20Hindu%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20also%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-set-to-inaugurate-first-hindu-temple-in-abu-dhabi-5056901%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-set-to-inaugurate-first-hindu-temple-in-abu-dhabi-5056901%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-set-to-inaugurate-first-hindu-temple-in-abu-dhabi-5056901%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Queen%20of%20Bones%E2%80%99%20Revi