704647.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fkyiv-sinks-russian-ship-off-crimea-in-blow-days-before-wars-2nd-anniversary%2Farticleshow%2F107704647.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fkyiv-sinks-russian-ship-off-crimea-in-blow-days-before-wars-2nd-anniversary%2Famp_articleshow%2F107704647.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fkyiv-sinks-russian-ship-off-crimea-in-blow-days-before-wars-2nd-anniversary%2Famp_articleshow%2F107704647.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%20Killed%2C%2021%20Injured%20In%20Mass%20Shooting%20At%20US%20Super%20Bowl%20Parade%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20was%20killed%20and%20multiple%20children%20were%20among%2021%20injured%20after%20a%20mass%20shooting%20at%20the%20Kansas%20City%20Chiefs'%20Super%20Bowl%20victory%20rally%20on%20Wednesday%20triggered%20panic%20among%20huge%20crowds%20of%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren's%20Mercy%20Hospital%20in%20Kansas%20City%2C%20which%20takes%20patients%20up%20to%20the%20age%20of%2017%2C%20said%20it%20was%20treating%2012%20people%20--%2011%20of%20them%20children%2C%20nine%20for%20gunshot%20wounds%20--%20after%20the%20shooting%2C%20which%20unfolded%20just%20moments%20after%20Chiefs%20players%20had%20addressed%20a%20vast%20crowd%20of%20cheering%20supporters%20gathered%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20three%20people%20had%20been%20taken%20into%20custody%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20but%20the%20motive%20and%20circumstances%20behind%20the%20shooting%20were%20still%20under%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKansas%20City%20fire%20department%20chief%20Ross%20Grundyson%20told%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20many%20of%20the%20victims%20had%20sustained%20%26quot%3Blife-threatening%20injuries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20eight%20what%20we%20considered%20immediately%20life-threatening%20patients%2C%20we%20had%20seven%20with%20life-threatening%20injuries%2C%20and%20had%20six%20that%20had%20minor%20injuries%2C%26quot%3B%20Grundyson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20shots%20rang%20out%2C%20shocked%20fans%20scrambled%20to%20flee%20to%20safety%20as%20police%20worked%20to%20clear%20Union%20Station%20in%20a%20tragic%20end%20to%20what%20had%20been%20a%20joyous%20morning%20of%20celebration%20to%20salute%20the%20NFL%20champions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaul%20Contreras%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20rally%20with%20his%20three%20daughters%2C%20said%20he%20tackled%20and%20disarmed%20one%20of%20the%20suspected%20shooters%20before%20the%20police%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20the%20right%20angle%20on%20him%20and%20I%20hit%20him%20from%20behind.%20And%20when%20I%20hit%20him%20from%20behind%2C%20I%20either%20jarred%20the%20gun%20out%20of%20his%20hand%20or%20out%20of%20his%20sleeve%2C%26quot%3B%20Contreras%20said%20on%20CNN.%20%26quot%3BI%20take%20him%20down%2C%20and%20I'm%20putting%20all%20my%20body%20weight%20on%20him.%20And%20then%20another%20good%20Samaritan%20comes%20over%20and%20is%20helping%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVictims%20were%20treated%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%20before%20being%20carried%20away%20on%20stretchers%20as%20crowds%20streamed%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20angry%20at%20what%20happened%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Kansas%20City%20Police%20chief%20Stacey%20Graves%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20who%20came%20to%20this%20celebration%20should%20expect%20a%20safe%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20chief%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKansas%20City%20mayor%20Quinton%20Lucas%20was%20among%20VIPs%20at%20the%20event%20who%20were%20sent%20running%20for%20cover%20after%20shots%20rang%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20day%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20look%20forward%20to.%20Something%20they%20remember%20for%20a%20lifetime.%20And%20what%20they%20shouldn't%20have%20to%20remember%20is%20the%20threat%20of%20gun%20violence%2C%26quot%3B%20Lucas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chiefs%20meanwhile%20condemned%20the%20shooting%20as%20senseless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20truly%20saddened%20by%20the%20senseless%20act%20of%20violence%20that%20occurred%20outside%20of%20Union%20Station%20at%20the%20conclusion%20of%20today's%20parade%20and%20rally%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20franchise%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPraying%20for%20Kansas%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20City%20Chiefs%20quarterback%20Patrick%20Mahomes%20wrote%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Huge%20crowds%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20moments%20before%20the%20shooting%2C%20Mahomes%20and%20his%20teammates%20had%20been%20soaking%20up%20the%20adulation%20from%20a%20sea%20of%20red-shirted%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20had%20been%20no%20hint%20of%20trouble%20as%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20partying%20supporters%20feted%20Chiefs%20players%20along%20a%20two-mile%20(three-kilometer)%20route%20in%20a%20procession%20of%20double-decker%20buses%2C%20enveloped%20by%20a%20blizzard%20of%20red%20and%20gold%20confetti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20officials%20said%20more%20than%20one%20million%20people%20were%20expected%20for%20the%20parade%2C%20which%20was%20held%20in%20unseasonably%20sunny%2C%20warm%20conditions%20in%20downtown%20Kansas%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGun%20violence%20is%20not%20uncommon%20at%20large-scale%20sporting%20victory%20celebrations%20in%20North%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%2010%20people%20were%20wounded%20after%20a%20shooting%20which%20erupted%20in%20Denver%20amid%20fans%20celebrating%20the%20Denver%20Nuggets'%20NBA%20championship%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20four%20people%20were%20injured%20after%20gunfire%20broke%20out%20near%20a%20parade%20to%20honor%20the%20Toronto%20Raptors'%20NBA%20