ion%20meds%2C%20and%20gender-affirming%20care%2C%20per%20the%20Mozilla%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20apps%20feature%20chatbots%20whose%20character%20descriptions%20feature%20violence%20or%20underage%20abuse%2C%20while%20others%20warned%20that%20the%20bots%20could%20be%20unsafe%20or%20hostile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mozilla%20Foundation%20noted%20that%20in%20the%20past%2C%20apps%20had%20encouraged%20dangerous%20behavior%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwidow-accuses-ai-chatbot-reason-husband-kill-himself-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Chai%20AI)%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-assassinate-queen-elizabeth-confided-plans-ai-chatbot-girlfriend-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eassassination%20attempt%20on%20the%20late%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Replika).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEva%20AI%20Chat%20Bot%20%26amp%3B%20Soulmate%20and%20CrushOn.AI%20didn't%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%20A%20representative%20for%20Replika%20told%20BI%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BReplika%20has%20never%20sold%20user%20data%20and%20does%20not%2C%20and%20has%20never%2C%20supported%20advertising%20either.%20The%20only%20use%20of%20user%20data%20is%20to%20improve%20conversations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20find%20the%20prospect%20of%20AI%20romance%20impossible%20to%20resist%2C%20the%20Mozilla%20Foundation%20urges%20several%20precautions%2C%20including%20not%20saying%20anything%20you%20wouldn't%20want%20a%20colleague%20or%20family%20member%20to%20read%2C%20using%20a%20strong%20password%2C%20opting%20out%20of%20AI%20training%2C%20and%20limiting%20the%20app's%20access%20to%20other%20mobile%20features%20such%20as%20your%20location%2C%20microphone%2C%20and%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20shouldn't%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20cool%20new%20technologies%20with%20your%20safety%20or%20your%20privacy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-girlfriends-romantic-chatbots-toxic-privacy-nightmare-experts-warn-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707957509000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd24966fcb546d2d4fe189%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-girlfriends-romantic-chatbots-toxic-privacy-nightmare-experts-warn-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Romantic%20chatbots%20foster%20a%20toxic%20dynamic%20and%20relentlessly%20pry%20user%20data%2C%20The%20Mozilla%20Foundation%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Geoff%20Weiss)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-girlfriends-romantic-chatbots-toxic-privacy-nightmare-experts-warn-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22X%20took%20payment%20from%20terrorists%2C%20campaigners%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707957379000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FE385%2Fproduction%2F_132654285_x.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68297121%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Campaigners%20at%20the%20Tech%20Transparency%20Project%20in%20the%20US%20found%20paid-for%20features%20for%20organisations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A90%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68297121%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68297121.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68297121.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sharon%20Stone%20Says%20Fame%20After%20%E2%80%98Basic%20Instinct%E2%80%99%20Got%20So%20Crazy%20That%20LA%20Police%20Put%20Her%20in%20L