0themselves%20%E2%80%9Cconsistently%20targeted%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20their%20association%20with%20the%20US%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20merely%20a%20week%20ago%2C%20they%20resisted%20political%20efforts%20by%20pro-Iran%20groups%20to%20expel%20US%20troops%20from%20Iraq.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIraqi%20Kurdistan%20expects%20the%20US%20to%20appreciate%20such%20stances%20and%20provide%20air%20defenses%2C%20given%20the%20high%20stakes%20for%20the%20autonomous%20region.%20That%20could%20either%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20US%20supplying%20such%20weaponry%20directly%20to%20the%20Peshmerga%20or%20having%20the%20US%20military%20expand%20its%20limited%20air%20defense%20capabilities%20in%20Iraqi%20Kurdistan%20to%20cover%20the%20region%20rather%20than%20just%20US%20bases%20and%20the%20American%20consulate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECeng%20Sagnic%2C%20chief%20of%20analysis%20of%20the%20geopolitical%20consultancy%20firm%20TAM-C%20Solutions%2C%20said%20%E2%80%9Cseveral%20considerations%E2%80%9D%20are%20involved%20in%20supplying%20the%20Peshmerga%20air%20defenses.%20In%20his%20view%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprimary%20concern%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20requirement%20under%20the%20current%20NDAA%20also%20to%20arm%20the%20Iraqi%20military%20with%20such%20systems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20US%20might%20hesitate%20to%20provide%20advanced%20weaponry%20to%20the%20central%20Iraqi%20government%2C%20especially%20given%20Baghdad%E2%80%99s%20inclination%20to%20formally%20request%20the%20departure%20of%20coalition%20forces%20from%20Iraq%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagnic%20told%20Insider.%20%E2%80%9CConsequently%2C%20the%20central%20Iraqi%20government%20might%20delay%20acquiring%20air%20defense%20systems%20from%20the%20US%20to%20prevent%20their%20delivery%20to%20the%20Kurdish%20region%20on%20guidance%20from%20Iran.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThreat%20perceptions%20in%20Baghdad%20and%20Iraqi%20Kurdistan%E2%80%99s%20Erbil%20also%20diffe