geted%20the%20SDF%20with%20drones.%20On%20Feb.%205%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fsyria-iraq-sdf-islamic-resistance-us-c621972db21d6b3db7ca1bccd50ce6ef%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Esix%20SDF%20fighters%20were%20killed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20when%20an%20explosive%20drone%20launched%20by%20an%20Iran-backed%20militia%20hit%20their%20base%2C%20which%20also%20houses%20US%20troops.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMazlum%20Kobane%2C%20the%20SDF%E2%80%99s%20commander%20in%20chief%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-backed-force-syria-more-air-defence-needed-after-deadly-drone-attack-2024-02-08%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20Reuters%20on%20Feb.%208%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20his%20forces%20%E2%80%9Crequire%20technical%20capabilities%20and%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20aerial%20defensive%20systems%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20900%20US%20troops%20in%20Syria%20have%20some%20limited%20defenses%2C%20including%20short-range%20Avenger%20systems%20that%20fire%20Stinger%20missiles.%20These%20defenses%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Fus-led-coalition-blocks-attacks-at-conoco-oil-field-in-syria-%2F7482765.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Eintercepted%20six%20incoming%20militia%20drones%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20Feb.%2010.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20US%20provision%20of%20such%20systems%20to%20the%20SDF%20would%20likely%20face%20opposition%20from%20Turkey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20recent%20clashes%20as%20a%20reason%20to%20request%20additional%20US%20air%20defenses%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20viewed%20negatively%20in%20Ankara%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ali%20Bakir%2C%20a%20Turkey%20expert%20and%20non-resident%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Atlantic