ed%20in%20the%20last%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20a%20state%20legislative%20assembly%20are%20eligible%20to%20receive%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20notification%2C%20electoral%20bonds%20shall%20be%20encashed%20by%20an%20eligible%20political%20party%20only%20through%20an%20account%20with%20an%20authorised%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202019%2C%20the%20Supreme%20court%20had%20declined%20to%20stay%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20and%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20would%20accord%20an%20in-depth%20hearing%20on%20the%20pleas%20as%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20had%20raised%20%26quot%3Bweighty%20issues%26quot%3B%20that%20had%20%26quot%3Btremendous%20bearing%20on%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20B%20R%20Gavai%2C%20J%20B%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20had%20on%20October%2031%20last%20year%20commenced%20hearing%20arguments%20on%20the%20four%20petitions%2C%20including%20those%20filed%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Jaya%20Thakur%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20and%20NGO%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20Supreme%20court%20had%20underscored%20the%20need%20for%20reducing%20the%20cash%20component%20in%20the%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707936780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-verdict-on-validity-of-electoral-bonds-scheme-tomorrow-5058604%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20scheduled%20to%20pronounce%20its%20verdict%20on%20Thursday%20on%20a%20batch%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-verdict-on-validity-of-electoral-bonds-scheme-tomorrow-5058604%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-verdict-on-validity-of-electoral-bonds-scheme-tomorrow-5058604%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-verdict-on-validity-of-electoral-bonds-scheme-tomorrow-5058604%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMeeting%20With%20Centre%20Today%20Won't%20Push%20Forward%20Until%20Then%26quot%3B%3A%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20will%20hold%20a%20meeting%20with%20farmers%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday%20and%20the%20protestors%20will%20remain%20peaceful%20and%20not%20try%20and%20push%20their%20way%20through%20the%20barricades%20and%20other%20barriers%20at%20various%20borders%20until%20then%2C%20a%20farmer%20leader%20has%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20senior%20police%20officers%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20said%20Union%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Arjun%20Munda%20and%20two%20other%20Union%20Ministers%2C%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20Nityanand%20Rai%2C%20will%20meet%20representatives%20of%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20in%20the%20city%20at%205%20pm%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%C2%A0Mr%20Goyal%20holds%20the%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution%20portfolio%20and%20Mr%20Rai%20is%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20a%20message%20we%20got%20last%20night%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur's%20call%20for%20dialogue%2C%20we%20spoke%20to%20everyone%20in%20the%20movement%20and%20decided%20that%20we%20would%20remain%20peaceful%20today%20and%20not%20try%20and%20push%20further%20from%20where%20we%20were.%20A%20meeting%20has%20been%20called%20for%205%20pm%20tomorrow%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20our%20peaceful%20protest.%20No%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20from%20our%20side%20until%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Pandher.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer%20leader%20alleged%2C%20however%2C%20that%20even%20though%20they%20held%20a%20peaceful%20protest%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20drones%20were%20used%20and%20tear%20gas%20shells%20and%20rubber%20pellets%20were%20fired%20at%20them.%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20the%20police%2C%20but%20paramilitary%20forces%20that%20were%20attacking%20us.%20Despite%20all%20this%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20Union%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Arjun%20Munda%20had%20called%20for%20dialogue%20and%20urged%20the%20farmers%20not%20to%20do%20anything%20that%20inconveniences%20common%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20all%20aspects%20and%20discuss%20this.%20The%20farmers%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20normal%20life%20is%20not%20disrupted.%20I%20think%20no%20solution%20can%20be%20found%20by%20doing%20anything%20that%20causes%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20common%20man.%20Such%20actions%20only%20create%20hurdles%20in%20finding%20a%20solution.%20I%20urge%20them%20to%20maintain%20a%20conducive%20atmosphere%20for%20dialogue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Union%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-navy-veterans-can-be-brought-back-anurag-thakur-on-talks-with-farmers-5052525%5C%22%3EAnurag%20Thakur%20had%20also%20called%20for%20discussions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stating%20that%20even%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans%20were%20brought%20back%20from%20Qatar%20throu