-complain-about-fake-dominos-pizza-outlets-on-swiggy-company-reacts-5058518%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bike%20taxis%20get%20Centre's%20legal%20kick-start%20paving%20way%20for%20new%20riding%20option%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707931763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-02%2F23%2Ffull%2F1677172864-1326.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fbike-taxis-get-centre-s-legal-kick-start-paving-way-for-new-riding-option-124021401789_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20move%20now%20allows%20motorcycles%20to%20operate%20legally%20as%20contract%20carriages%20in%20India%2C%20potentially%20opening%20up%20new%20transportation%20options%20and%20income%20opportunities%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fbike-taxis-get-centre-s-legal-kick-start-paving-way-for-new-riding-option-124021401789_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fbike-taxis-get-centre-s-legal-kick-start-paving-way-for-new-riding-option-124021401789_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fbike-taxis-get-centre-s-legal-kick-start-paving-way-for-new-riding-option-124021401789_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20%26quot%3BDome%20Of%20Harmony%26quot%3B%20Inside%20Sanctum%20Sanctorum%20Of%20Abu%20Dhabi%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMarking%20a%20significant%20milestone%20for%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20inaugurated%20Abu%20Dhabi's%20first%20Hindu%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20also%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpread%20over%2027%20acres%20and%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20over%20Rs%20700%20crore%2C%20the%20BAPS%20Hindu%20temple%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20deepening%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20participated%20in%20a%20'global%20aarti%20(prayer)'%2C%20which%20was%20performed%20simultaneously%20at%20over%201%2C200%20temples%20built%20by%20BAPS.%20The%20Bochasanwasi%20Shri%20Akshar%20Purushottam%20Swaminarayan%20Hindu%20Mandir%20or%20BAPS%20Hindu%20Mandir%2C%20is%20spread%20over%20a%2027-acre%20piece%20of%20land.%20The%20temple%20is%20108%20feet%20high%20and%20180%20feet%20wide%20and%20its%20seven%20spires%20represent%20the%20seven%20emirates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20has%20402%20pillars%20and%20iron%20has%20not%20been%20used%20in%20any%20of%20them%2C%20making%20it%20the%20first%20Hindu%20stone%20temple%20in%20UAE.%20The%20pillars%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20temple%20are%20made%20of%20white%20Italian%20marble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pillars%20have%20intricate%20carvings%20of%20deities%20and%20symbols%20central%20to%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%20Seven%20shrines%20of%20different%20deities%20including%2C%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20Goddess%20Sita%2C%20Lakshmi%2C%20and%20Lord%20Shiv%2C%20are%20present%20in%20the%20temple.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDome%20of%20Harmony%20has%20different%20levels.%20These%20levels%20represent%20the%20fire%2C%20earth%2C%20air%2C%20water%20and%20space.%20The%20shank%20represents%20water%2C%20Tej%20represents%20the%20sun%20and%20running%20Deers%20represent%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20volunteer%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20pillar%20inside%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20is%20unique%20and%20every%20pillar%20has%20its%20pillar.%20There%20are%201%2C400%20pillars%2C%20protected%20by%20a%20transparent%20shield.%20They%20represent%20differences%2C%20but%20they%20all%20make%20one%20pillar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20volunteer%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20depiction%20of%20different%20civilizations%20on%20pillars%20makes%20the%20temple's%20architecture%20unique.%20Apart%20from%20Indian%20civilization%2C%20stories%20are%20taken%20from%20the%20Maya%2C%20Aztec%2C%20Egyptian%2C%20Arabic%2C%20European%2C%20Chinese%20and%20African%20civilizations%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shrine%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Goddess%20Sita%2C%20the%20Ramayan%20has%20been%20carved%20on%20the%20stones%20and%20'shankh'%20(shell)%20and%20sun%20have%20been%20sculpted%20on%20the%20dome%20of%20the%20shrine.%20The%20Vedic-style%20temple%20has%20two%20central%20domes%20-%20the%20'Dome%20of%20Harmony'%20and%20the%20'Dome%20of%20Peace'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fine%20detailing%20in%20sculpting%20the%20deities%20and%20symbols%20makes%20the%20temple%20an%20architectural%20brilliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707931680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F0icj1ua8_dome-of-harmony_625x300_14_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwatch-dome-of-harmony-inside-sanctum-sanctorum-of-abu-dhabis-baps-temple-5058682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Marking%20a%20significant%20milestone%20for%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20inaugurated%20Abu%20Dhabi's%20first%20Hindu%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20also%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwatch-dome-of-harmony-inside-sanctum-sanctorum-of-abu-dhabis-baps-temple-5058682%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwatch-dome-of-harmony-inside-sanctum-sanctorum-of-abu-dhabis-baps-temple-5058682%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwatch-dome-of-harmony-inside-sanctum-sanctorum-of-abu-dhabis-baps-temple-5058682%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Are%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon%20heading%20for%20war%3F%2