ster%20said%20a%20large%20number%20of%20devotees%20will%20visit%20the%20temple%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20and%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20his%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20to%20President%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUAE%2C%20which%20till%20now%20was%20known%20for%20Burj%20Khalifa%2C%20Future%20Museum%2C%20Sheikh%20Zayed%20Mosque%20and%20other%20hi-tech%20buildings%2C%20has%20now%20added%20another%20cultural%20chapter%20to%20its%20identity.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20a%20large%20number%20of%20devotees%20will%20come%20here%20in%20the%20coming%20times.%20This%20will%20also%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20people%20coming%20to%20UAE%20and%20people-to-people%20connections%20will%20also%20increase.%20On%20behalf%20of%20the%20entire%20India%20and%20millions%20of%20Indians%20living%20around%20the%20world%2C%20I%20express%20my%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20to%20President%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%20and%20the%20UAE%20Government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20the%20gathering%20to%20give%20a%20standing%20ovation%20to%20the%20UAE%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majestic%20Bochasanwasi%20Akshar%20Purushottam%20Swaminarayan%20Sanstha%20(BAPS)%20Mandir%2C%20the%20first%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20his%20arrival%20at%20the%20temple%20premises%2C%20PM%20Modi%20was%20welcomed%20by%20BAPS'%20Ishwarcharandas%20Swami.%20He%20offered%20prayers%20at%20the%20temple%20and%20performed%20aarti.%20The%20temple%20was%20inaugurated%20on%20the%20auspicious%20occasion%20of%20Basant%20Panchmi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20BAPS%20Hindu%20Temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20was%20held%20ahead%20of%20its%20inauguration.%20The%20priests%20conducted%20rituals%20before%20the%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20UAE%20on%20Tuesday%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20and%20talked%20about%20the%20BAPS%20temple%20at%20the%20'Ahlan%20Modi'%20diaspora%20event%20held%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20thanked%20the%20UAE%20President%20for%20giving%20approval%20for%20the%20BAPS%20Hindu%20Mandir%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20reflects%20his%20love%20and%20respect%20for%20India%20and%20couldn't%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20his%20love%20and%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Mandir%2C%20the%20first%20traditional%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20sits%20on%2027%20acres%20of%20land%20that%20was%20generously%20gifted%20by%20the%20UAE%20leadership.The%20estimated%20cost%20of%20this%20magnificent%20construction%2C%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20devotion%20and%20commitment%20of%20the%20community%2C%20is%20Dh400%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BAPS%20Hindu%20Mandir%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20architectural%20brilliance%20and%20cultural%20significance%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20region%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20stone%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20the%20area%2C%20proudly%20standing%20as%20the%20largest%20in%20West%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESituated%20in%20the%20Abu%20Mureikhah%20area%2C%20this%20majestic%20structure%20embodies%20the%20spirit%20of%20cultural%20peace%20and%20collaboration%20and%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20enduring%20friendship%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20UAE%20also%20marks%20the%20third%20by%20the%20PM%20to%20the%20Gulf%20country%20in%20the%20past%20eight%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707928560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F02pergjg_uae-temple_625x300_14_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsymbol-of-unity-harmony-pm-modi-after-inaugurating-hindu-temple-in-abu-d