20governor%20of%20Jakarta%2C%20and%20Ganjar%20Pranowo%20from%20the%20Indonesian%20Democratic%20Party%20of%20Struggle%2C%20had%20around%C2%A025%25%20and%2016%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20according%20to%20Kompas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20numbers%20were%20published%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20Ganjar%20said%20the%20politician%E2%80%99s%20team%20had%20received%20reports%20of%20%E2%80%9Cstructural%2C%20systematic%20and%20massive%20fraud%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20investigating%20them.%20Separately%2C%20Ganjar%20said%20he%20and%20his%20aides%20will%20%E2%80%9Cwait%20for%20election%20results%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPrivate%20pollsters%20count%20the%20votes%20at%20a%20sample%20of%20polling%20stations%20around%20the%20country.%20These%20are%20called%20%E2%80%9Cquick%20counts%E2%80%9D.%20In%20previous%20elections%2C%20counts%20by%20reputable%20pollsters%20have%20proven%20accurate.%20Official%20results%20are%20not%20expected%20for%20several%20weeks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2F200-million-voters-and-820000-polling-stations-indonesias-massive-election-in-numbers%5C%22%3E200%20Million%20Voters%20and%20820%2C000%20Polling%20Stations%3A%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20Massive%20Election%20in%20Numbers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorld%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20single-day%20election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolls%20have%20closed%20in%20Indonesia%20for%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20single-day%20election%C2%A0that%20will%20see%20a%20new%20president%20succeed%20Joko%20Widodo%2C%20also%20known%20as%20President%20Jokowi.%20The%20voters%20are%20also%20deciding%20on%20new%20lawmakers%20and%20parliamentarians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20took%20place%20across%20three%20times%20zones%20with%20polling%20stations%20opening%20at%207%3A00%20am%20(2200%20GMT)%20in%20the%20easternmost%20region%20of%20Papua%20and%20closing%20at%2001%3A00%20pm%20(0600%20GMT)%20at%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20country%20in%20jungle-clad%20Sumatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThunderstorms%20caused%20flooding%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20capital%2C%20Jakarta%2C%20with%20Reuters%20news%20agency%20reporting%20that%20dozens%20of%20polling%20stations%20had%20been%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20the%20main%20contenders%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20race%20for%20the%20presidency%20has%20seen%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwho-are-indonesias-presidential-hopefuls%2Fa-67267495%5C%22%3Ethree%20main%20candidates%20emerge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20opinion%20polls%20ahead%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20the%20man%20leading%20the%20race%20is%20Prabowo%20Subianto%20from%20the%20Gerindra%20Party%2C%20a%20former%20military%20commander%20who%20currently%20serves%20as%20the%20minister%20of%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabowo%20is%20up%20against%20Ganjar%20Pranowo%20from%20the%20Indonesian%20Democratic%20Party%20of%20Struggle%20and%20Anies%20Baswedan%2C%20the%20former%20governor%20of%20Jakarta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndonesia%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20third-largest%20democracy%20with%20around%20205%20million%20voters%20eligible%20to%20cast%20ballots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbiggest-election-year-2024%5C%22%3EIndia%2C%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%A6Is%202024%20the%20Biggest%20Election%20Year%20Ever%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20at%20stake%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Southeast%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20largest%20economy%2C%C2%A0Indonesia%C2%A0has%20experienced%20stability%20and%20growth%20under%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%20All%20three%20presidential%20contenders%20have%20made%20similar%20promises%20to%20continue%20in%20that%20vein.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProbowo%20is%20the%20only%20candidate%20with%20ties%20to%20the%C2%A0era%20of%20Suharto%20dicatorship%2C%20a%20time%20marked%20by%20brutality%20and%20corruption.%20He%20was%20a%20special%20forces%20commander%20during%20that%20period%20and%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20human%20rights%20atrocities%2C%20which%20he%20strongly%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20concerns%20that%20a%20Probowo%20presidency%20could%20see%20a%20backslide%20towards%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20authoritarian%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20changes%20would%20have%20ramifications%20beyond%20Indonesia%2C%20as%20Jakarta%20wields%20a%20significant%20diplomatic%20influence%20among%20its%20Southeast%20Asian%20neighbours%20and%20boasts%20strong%20trade%20relationships%20with%20China%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findonesia-elections-prabowo-subianto-claims-victory%2Fa-68251339%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3EDW%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707927437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14214333%2FPrabowo-III.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fprabowo-subianto-claims-victory-indonesia-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Independent%20pollster%20Litbang%20Kompas%20said%20that%20Subianto%20was%20leading%20with%20nearly%2060%25%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20based%20on%20over%20half%20of%20the%20votes%20counted%20at%20a%20sample%20of%20polling%20stations%20across%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fprabowo-subianto-claims-victory-indonesia-election%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nabard%20Q3%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20rises%2034%25%20to%20Rs%204%2C495%20crore%2C%20income%20up%2025%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707927147000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F