%2C%22published%22%3A1707920154000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FFF8A%2Fproduction%2F_118781456_mediaitem118781455.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68282228%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Nigerian%20court%20hears%20dramatic%20testimony%20in%20the%20corruption%20trial%20of%20the%20former%20central%20bank%20chief.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A286%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68282228%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68282228.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68282228.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Demolitions%20as%20Extra-Judicial%20Punishment%20Have%20Left%20India%20in%20a%20Perpetual%20State%20of%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20demolitions%20in%20Uttarakhand%20last%20week%2C%20after%20which%20five%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20violence%2C%20follows%20a%20pattern%20that%20we%20see%20in%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-ruled%20states.%20The%20pattern%20is%20of%20course%20that%20the%20government%20goes%20after%20citizens%2C%20especially%20Muslims.%20The%20demolitions%20are%20carried%20out%20as%20a%20form%20of%20extra-judicial%20punishment%20by%20the%20municipal%20authorities%20and%20the%20police%2C%20whether%20after%20episodes%20of%20communal%20violence%20or%20protests%20against%20discrimination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pattern%20has%20been%20documented%20in%20reports%20like%20%E2%80%9CRoutes%20of%20Wrath%3A%20Weaponising%20religious%20processions%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Citizens%20and%20Lawyers%20Initiative.%20In%20his%20foreword%2C%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Rohinton%20F.%20Nariman%20says%20the%20report%20corroborates%20the%20findings%20(of%20decline%20in%20Indian%20democratic%20values)%2C%20adding%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20finds%20that%20in%20nine%20states%2C%20during%20Ram%20Navami%20and%20Hanuman%20Jayanti%20celebrations%20in%20April%202022%2C%20there%20were%20widespread%20acts%20of%20hooliganism%20and%20violence.%E2%80%9D%20After%20this%2C%20the%20JCBs%20came%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20report%20by%20Amnesty%20International%2C%20of%20which%20I%20am%20India%20chair%2C%20has%20found%20similar%20patterns%20of%20people%20made%20homeless%20and%20deprived%20of%20livelihoods.%20These%20individuals%20were%20subjected%20to%20forced%20evictions%2C%20intimidation%20and%20unlawful%20force%20by%20the%20police%20and%20collective%20and%20arbitrary%20punishment%2C%20which%20undermined%20their%20rights%20to%20non-discrimination%2C%20adequate%20housing%2C%20and%20a%20fair%20trial.%20Muslim-concentrated%20localities%20were%20either%20chosen%20or%20Muslim-owned%20properties%20selectively%20targeted%20in%20diverse%20areas%20for%20demolitions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdjacent%20or%20nearby%20Hindu-owned%20properties%20that%20also%20allegedly%20encroached%20on%20public%20land%2C%20particularly%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20were%20left%20untouched.%20The%20Indian%20state%E2%80%99s%20rationalisation%20of%20carrying%20out%20arbitrary%20demolitions%20to%20remove%20illegal%20encroachment%20sits%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20country%20where%20the%20implementation%20of%20building%20laws%20sees%20lack%20of%20enforcement%2C%20that%20has%20led%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20construction%20without%20requisite%20permissions.%20In%202017%2C%20a%20report%20by%20a%20panel%20formed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20to%20document%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20constructions%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20capital%20region%20found%20%E2%80%9C90%20per%20cent%20(of%20buildings)%20carry%20one%20kind%20of%20violation%20of%20the%20building%20bylaws%20or%20another%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20emblematic%20case%20here%20is%20that%20of%20Sainik%20Farms%20in%20Delhi%2C%20a%20tiny%20enclave%20that%20is%20totally%20illegal%20but%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20seen%20any%20JCBs%20come%20and%20demolish%20the%20bungalows%20of%20our%20wealthy.%20The%20headline%20of%20a%20May%202023%20news%20item%20illustrates%20this%20perfectly%3A%20%E2%80%9CExpedite%20call%20on%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Sainik%20Farms%E2%80%99%20bid%20for%20regularisation%3A%20High%20Court%E2%80%9D.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20poor%20and%20especially%20Muslim%20poor%20are%20not%20given%20any%20such%20leeway.%20They%E2%80%99re%20subjected%20to%20forced%20eviction%2C%20which%20is%20the%20permanent%20or%20temporary%20removal%20of%20people%20against%20their%20will%20from%20the%20homes%20or%20land%20they%20occupy%2C%20without%20legal%20protections%20and%20other%20safeguards.%20Forced%20evictions%20are%20a%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%2C%20including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20right%20to%20adequate%20housing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslims-targeted-in-128-demolitions-617-people-affected-amnesty-reports-on-bulldozer-action%5C%22%3EMuslims%20Targeted%20in%20128%20Demolitions%2C%20617%20People%20Affected%E2%80%99%3A%20Amnesty%20Reports%20on%20Bulldozer%20Action%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20international%20human%20rights%20law%2C%20states%20must%20ensure%20that%20evictions%20only%20occur%20in%20exceptional%20circumstances%2C%20require%20full%20justification%20and%20the%20provision%20of%20adequate%20legal%20safeguards.%20None%20of%20that%20here%20in%20New%20India%2C%20of%20course.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20bulldozer%20demolitions%20are%20often%20instigated%20at%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20government%2C%20with%20many%20state%20officials%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20calling%20for%20the%20use%20of%20bulldozers%20against%20Muslims.%20There%20is%20credible%20evidence%20to%20believe%20these%20demolitions%20are%20discriminatory%20and%20targeted%20as%20part%20of%20a%20hate%20campaign%20against%20Muslims%20in%20India.%20Rather%20than%20prevent%20discrimination%20towards%20Muslims%2C%20senior%20political%20leaders%20and%20officials%20have%20actively%20encouraged%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20April%202022%20demolitions%20in%20Delhi%2C%20BJP%20spokesman%20G.V.L.%20Narasimha%20defined%20JCB%20as%20%E2%80%9CJihadi%20Control%20Board%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20a%20now-deleted%20tweet.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20discrimination%20shows%20elsewhere%20too.%20A%20year-and-a-half%20since%20the%20demolitions%20that%20Amnesty%20documented%2C%20despite%20the%20financial%20hardships%20created%20by%20the%20loss%20of%20their%20homes%20and%20businesses%2C%20victims%20continue%20to%20wait%20for%20justice%20with%20legal%20cases%20pending%20in%20courts.%20To%20date%2C%20the%20courts%20have%20failed%20to%20address%20punitive%20demolitions%20with%20the%20scale%20and%20urgency%20required%20by%20the%20prevailing%20situation%2C%20enabling%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20continue%20tearing%20down%20people%E2%80%99s%20homes%20and%20businesses%20in%20other%20areas%20with%20widespread%20impunity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20must%20be%20seen%20in%20conjunction%20with%20the%20creation%20of%20quasi-judicial%20tribunals%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20which%20have%20provided%20prompt%20relief%20to%20Hindus%20who%20suffered%20losses%20due%20to%20the%20preceding%20violence%20while%20Muslim%20victims%20of%20the%20violence%20and%20following%20demolitions%20continue%20to%20struggle%20for%20justice.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%9CRoutes%20of%20Wrath%E2%80%9D%20report%20concludes%20that%20while%20there%20have%20been%20earlier%20phases%20of%20communal%20violence%20in%20India%2C%20which%20entrenched%20cycles%20of%20violence%2C%20segregation%20and%20generated%20lasting%20barriers%20to%20socio-economic%20mobility%20for%20Indian%20Muslims%20in%20particular%2C%20they%20did%20not%20undermine%20State%20control%20over%20society%20or%20its%20authority%20over%20institutions%20in%20the%20manner%20that%20is%20being%20seen%20today.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECoordination%20between%20Hindutva%20outfits%2C%20and%20the%20police%20and%20district%20administration%2C%20means%20combining%20an%20extreme%20ideological%20entity%20with%20the%20civil%20service.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20can%20be%20observed%20is%20that%20the%20relationship%20between%20them%20has%20become%20institutionalised%20in%20many%20parts%2C%20sustaining%20a%20violently%20undemocratic%20model%20of%20governance%20that%20is%20anathema%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20April%202022%2C%20more%20than%20100%20retired%20senior%20civil%20servants%20stated%20that%20the%20administration%20of%20law%20has%20become%20the%20means%20by%20which%20the%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20Muslims%2C%20can%20be%20kept%20in%20a%20state%20of%20perpetual%20fear.%20They%20said%20facilitation%20and%20support%20for%20communal%20frenzy%20was%20being%20provided%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20the%20administration%20%E2%80%94%20from%20local%20police%20and%20administrative%20officials%20to%20the%20highest%20political%20levels%20in%20state%20and%20Central%20governments.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20actual%20commission%20of%20violence%20may%20be%20outsourced%20to%20fringe%20groups%2C%20there%20is%20little%20doubt%20as%20to%20how%20the%20ground%20for%20their%20operations%20is%20made%20fertile%2C%20how%20each%20of%20them%20follows%20a%20master%20script%20and%20shares%20a%20common%20%E2%80%98tool%20kit%E2%80%99%20and%20how%20the%20propaganda%20machinery%20of%20a%20party%20as%20well%20as%20the%20State%20is%20made%20available%20to%20them%20to%20defend%20their%20actions%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20retired%20bureaucrats%20had%20written.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20the%20Citizens%20and%20Lawyers%20Initiative%20report%20concludes%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20available%20evidence%20corroborates%20statements%20by%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20lawyers%2C%20academics%20and%20activists%2C%20that%20India%20has%20now%20reached%20a%20stage%20of%20perpetual%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20an%20author%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707919218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdemolitions-as-extra-judicial-punishment-have-left-india-in-a-perpetual-state-of-violence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Under%20international%20human%20rights%20law%2C%20states%20must%20ensure%20that%20evictions%20only%20occur%20in%20exceptional%20circumstances%2C%20require%20full%20justification%20and%20the%20provision%20of%20adequate%20legal%20safeguards.%20None%20of%20that%20here%20in%20New%20India%2C%20of%20course.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdemolitions-as-extra-judicial-punishment-have-left-india-in-a-perpetual-state-of-violence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20hospitals%20'completely%20overwhelmed'%3A%20WHO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707917643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107696267%2Cimgsize-10518.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fgaza-hospitals-completely-overwhelmed-who%2Farticleshow%2F107696075.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107696075.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fgaza-hospitals-completely-overwhelmed-who%2Farticleshow%2F107696075.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fgaza-hospitals-completely-overwhelmed-who%2Famp_articleshow%2F107696075.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fgaza-hospitals-completely-overwhelmed-who%2Famp_articleshow%2F107696075.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sangolli%20Rayanna%3A%20The%20Forgotten%20Martyrdom%20of%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20Brave%20Peasant%20Leader%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14152907%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-14-at-3.28.09-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20event%20which%20took%20place%20on%20January%2026%2C%201831%20is%20either%20forgotten%20or%20belittled.%20Sangolli%20Rayanna%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20peasant%20army%2C%20who%20fought%20against%20not%20only%20the%20British%20but%20also%20feudal%20landlords%20was%20hanged%20by%20the%20British%20after%20being%20betrayed%20by%20the%20henchmen%20of%20local%20landlords%20on%20January%2026%2C%201831.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20India%20is%20at%20the%20verge%20of%20becoming%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Rajya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%2C%20an%20euphemism%20for%20the%20tyranny%20of%20Brahminical%20and%20capitalist%20rule%2C%20the%20valiant%20struggle%20of%20Rayanna%20is%20also%20being%20misrepresented%20as%20a%20battle%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20monarchical%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20systemic%20efforts%20to%20reduce%20him%20to%20the%20status%20of%20a%20leader%20of%20a%20caste%20group%20by%20the%20contemporary%20casteist%20monarchs%20and%20thereby%20erase%20the%20memory%20of%20a%20great%20chapter%20in%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20anti-colonial%20and%20anti-feudal%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20just%20a%20Kuruba%20leader%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20modern%20era%2C%20politics%20driven%20by%20caste%20is%20diminishing%20the%20stature%20of%20towering%20leaders%20into%20narrow%20confines%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20commits%20a%20betrayal%20to%20both%20history%20and%20the%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepicting%20Tipu%20Sultan%20as%20only%20a%20Muslim%20leader%2C%20presenting%20Rayanna%20as%20only%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Kuruba%20community%20and%20Ambedkar%20as%20only%20a%20Dalit%20leader%20are%20the%20outcomes%20of%20this%20systemic%20casteist%20politics.%20The%20modern%20lords%20who%20exploit%20communities%2C%20erect%20statues%20of%20historical%20figures%2C%20claiming%20them%20as%20leaders%20of%20their%20respective%20communities%20in%20a%20deceptive%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20part%20of%20this%20agenda%2C%20these%20modern%20rulers%20depict%20Rayanna%20solely%20as%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Kuruba%20community.%20But%20Rayanna%20mobilised%20exploited%20peasants%20of%20all%20the%20sections%20against%20the%20British%20and%20their%20local%20lords%20three%20decades%20before%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20war%20of%20Indian%20Independence%E2%80%9D%20in%201857%20by%20mobilising%20oppressed%20peasants%20from%20various%20communities%20including%20Kuruba%2C%20Beda%2C%20Jain%2C%20Lingayat%2C%20Siddhi%2C%20Muslim%20and%20Panchamasali%20in%20Kittur%20region%20of%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time%20he%20built%20a%20formidable%20patriotic%20and%20anti-feudal%20army%20of%20peasants%20and%20landless%20which%20became%20a%20nightmare%20for%20the%20British%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaketh%20Rajan%2C%20a%20great%20scholar%20and%20revolutionary%2C%20who%20studied%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20history%20extensively%20and%20died%20a%20martyr%20for%20a%20similar%20cause%20in%202005%20pointed%20out%20in%20his%20book%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMaking%20History%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20that%20Rayanna%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20was%20not%20just%20for%20the%20landless%20but%20also%20for%20the%20oppressed%20communities.%20Rayanna%20was%20cognizant%20of%20caste%20hierarchy%20among%20the%20oppressed%20peasants%20also.%20Saketh%20explained%20how%20he%20implemented%20a%20system%20of%20%3Cem%3Edasoha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93collective%20sharing%20of%20food%E2%80%93to%20eliminate%20caste%20differences%20and%20built%20a%20bond%20of%20fraternity%20among%20his%20warriors.%20This%20fact%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20Rayanna%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20beyond%20caste%20and%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20peasant%20commander%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accolades%20that%20the%20opportunistic%20politicians%20of%20the%20current%20times%20shower%20on%20Rayanna%20and%20the%20manner%20is%20which%20they%20choose%20to%20honour%20this%20great%20leader%20is%20appalling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%202010%2C%20then%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20while%20unveiling%20Rayanna%E2%80%99s%20statue%2C%20announced%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20awarding%20police%20officers%20who%20have%20rendered%20exceptional%20service%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Rayanna%2C%20we%20honour%20the%20sacrifice%2C%20devotion%20and%20loyalty%20of%20Rayanna%2C%20the%20soldier%20of%20Rani%20Kittur%20Chennamma.%E2%80%9D%20Thus%2C%20Rayanna%E2%80%99s%20virtue%20for%20these%20modern%20feudal%20lords%20was%20not%20his%20uncompromising%20and%20assertive%20anti%20feudalism%20but%20just%20loyalty%2C%20devotion%20and%20sacrifice%20as%20a%20soldier%20to%20the%20kingdom%20of%20high%20priests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20kings%20and%20chieftains%20fought%20against%20the%20British%2C%20primarily%20to%20preserve%20their%20sovereignty.%20But%2C%20Rayanna%20was%20not%20a%20chieftain%20or%20a%20prince.%20He%20was%20a%20soldier%20in%20the%20army%20of%20queen%20Chennamma%20of%20Kittur%20principality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%201857%2C%20many%20like%20Kittur%20Chennamma%20and%20Lakshmibai%2C%20although%20from%20royal%20families%2C%20refused%20to%20succumb%20to%20humiliating%20treaties%20offered%20by%20the%20British%20and%20chose%20to%20fight%20and%20die%20honourably.%20However%2C%20after%20learning%20lessons%20from%20the%20rebellion%20of%201857%2C%20the%20British%20ensured%20comfort%20and%20luxuries%20of%20the%20kings.%20Most%20kings%20then%20refrained%20from%20joining%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20after%201857.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20many%20betrayed%20their%20people%20to%20retain%20the%20tutelage%20of%20British%20rulers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20British%2C%20through%20its%20draconian%20policy%20of%20subsidiary%20alliance%20hatched%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20annex%20the%20Kittur%20kingdom%2C%20after%20the%20demise%20of%20the%20ruler%20Mallasarja%2C%20husband%20of%20Chennamma.%20She%20fought%20against%20the%20British%20but%20was%20captured%20and%20imprisoned%20and%20subsequently%20died%20on%20February%2021%2C%201829.%20Rayanna%20was%20witness%20to%20the%20imprisonment%20of%20Chennamma%20whom%20he%20met%20during%20her%20confinement%20in%20Bailhongal%2C%20posing%20as%20a%20peasant%20relative%20of%20hers%2C%20and%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20her%20longing%20for%20the%20repossession%20of%20Kittur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20capture%20of%20Chennamma%2C%20the%20British%20introduced%20barbaric%20land%20revenue%20system%20which%20pauperised%20the%20peasantry%20and%20empowered%20the%20corrupt%20upper%20caste%20record%20keeping%20Kualakarnis%20and%20the%20feudatories%20of%20the%20British%20rule.%20Rayanna%20himself%20being%20the%20victim%20of%20the%20new%20regime%20retreated%20into%20the%20forests%20and%20built%20an%20army%20of%20exploited%20peasants%20guerrillas%20against%20the%20British%20and%20subsequently%20against%20Landlords.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fbirsa-munda-social-reformer-revolutionary-leader%5C%22%3ERemembering%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20the%20Social%20Reformer%20and%20Revolutionary%20Leader%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuerrilla%20warfare%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20just%20a%20hundred%20men%20in%20the%20early%201830%2C%20his%20army%20grew%20to%205%2C000%20within%20months.%20Due%20to%20its%20constant%20fight%20against%20oppressors%2C%20it%20quickly%20took%20the%20form%20of%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20army%20and%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaketh%20Rajan%20through%20his%20wide%20field%20work%20and%20meticulous%20and%20laborious%20library%20work%20provides%20a%20glimpse%20in%20volume%20two%20of%20%3Cem%3EMaking%20History%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20how%20Sangolli%20Rayanna%20operated%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThus%20the%20people%20were%20mobilised%20in%20armed%20actions%20that%20Rayanna%20led.%20Of%20the%20innumerable%20such%20actions%20that%20the%20guerrillas%20initiated%2C%20most%20were%20attacks%20on%20government%20property%2C%20burning%20of%20the%20new%20land%20records%20and%20the%20extraction%20of%20returns%20from%20notorious%20landlords%20and%20bureaucrats%20who%20had%20pillaged%20the%20people%20consequent%20to%20the%20onset%20of%20British%20rule.%20The%20fact%20that%20people%20participated%20in%20large%20numbers%20in%20these%20actions%20goes%20to%20demonstrate%20not%20just%20that%20guerrillas%20were%20addressing%20the%20burning%20issues%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20but%20also%20that%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20mobilised%20the%20peasantry%20in%20such%20large%20numbers%20that%20no%20sooner%20that%20an%20action%20had%20been%20conducted%20and%20the%20guerrillas%20planned%20to%20leave%20the%20spot%2C%20they%20had%20already%20spontaneously%20recruited%20fighters%20for%20their%20cause.%20The%20raid%20on%20Sampgaon%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20pattern%20in%20their%20armed%20actions%20thus%20explains%20the%20rapid%20growth%20of%20Rayanna%E2%80%99s%20force.%20Popular%20support%20for%20Rayanna%E2%80%99s%20armed%20uprising%20was%20also%20expressed%20in%20the%20noncooperation%20of%20the%20people%20and%20particularly%20the%20other%20%3Cem%3Eshetsanadis%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20refused%20to%20share%20intelligence%20about%20Rayanna%E2%80%99s%20movements%20with%20the%20government.%20When%20government%20forces%20were%20on%20his%20pursuit%20after%20the%20raid%20on%20Sampgaon%2C%20Nisbet%2C%20the%20Collector%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Amildar%20and%20others%20repeat%20that%20the%20peons%20of%20some%20of%20the%20villages%20in%20that%20part%20of%20the%20country%20did%20not%20afford%20any%20assistance%20against%20the%20insurgents.%20They%20appear%20to%20act%20in%20concert%20with%20them%2C%20furnishing%20them%20with%20information%20and%20offering%20no%20resistance%20to%20their%20attacks%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20Rayanna%20was%20indeed%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20oppressed%20masses%20and%20a%20great%20leader%20of%20the%20peasant%20army.%20His%20sacrifice%20in%20the%20battle%20was%20not%20as%20a%20soldier%20or%20commander%20of%20a%20king%E2%80%99s%20army%2C%20but%20a%20conscious%20sacrifice%20for%20the%20people%2C%20to%20build%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20army.%20Therefore%2C%20realising%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20capture%20Rayanna%20through%20direct%20combat%2C%20the%20British%20conspired%20with%20the%20landlord%20class.%20They%20infiltrated%20his%20army%20with%20a%20landlord%20named%20Krishnarao.%20The%20result%20was%20betrayal%2C%20Rayanna%E2%80%99s%20capture%2C%20and%20his%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERewards%20for%20traitors%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnarao%20was%20rewarded%20with%20money%20for%20aiding%20in%20Rayanna%E2%80%99s%20capture.%20The%20landlords%20who%20betrayed%20the%20peasant%20struggle%20were%20also%20awarded.%20They%20received%20cash%20rewards%20and%20entire%20villages%20as%20gifts%20from%20the%20British%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Linganna%20Gowda%20received%20the%20village%20of%20Kaloli%20near%20Kittur%2C%20Yenkan%20Gowda%20got%20the%20village%20of%20Dhong%20near%20Dharwad.%20But%20Rayanna%20and%20his%20companions%20from%20various%20communities%2C%20including%20Kuruba%2C%20Beda%2C%20Jain%2C%20Lingayat%2C%20Siddhi%2C%20Muslim%20and%20Panchamasali%2C%20faced%20execution.%C2%A0These%20gifts%20by%20the%20British%20were%20also%20honoured%20by%20the%20independent%20India%20and%20thus%20the%20betrayers%20continued%20as%20new%20rulers%20in%20the%20new%20regime%20both%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Kittur.%20Whereas%20Rayanna%2C%20his%20memory%20and%20martyrdom%20is%20either%20belittled%20or%20erased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20same%20Brahminical-landlord-capitalist%20system%20%2C%20repacked%20as%20%3Cem%3ERamarajya-Modirajya%3C%2Fem%3E%20continues%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20republic.%20The%20cruel%20role%20played%20by%20loyalist%20police%20officers%20in%20suppressing%20people%20in%20this%20highly%20anti-people%20administration%20is%20being%20honoured%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20Sangolli%20Rayanna.%20They%20are%20disrespecting%20Rayanna%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20by%20awarding%20such%20prizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20when%20January%2026%20is%20paraded%20as%20the%20demonstration%20of%20military%20prowess%20of%20the%20new%20%3Cem%3ERam%20Rajya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20is%20absolutely%20necessary%20to%20remind%20the%20martyrdom%20of%20Rayana%20who%20dreamt%20of%20new%20people%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Eraj%3C%2Fem%3E%20%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshambhuka%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%3Cem%3E%20sita%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3Eraj%20but%20was%20hanged%20to%20death%20on%20January%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fshi