nship%5D%2C%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20happen%20automatically.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20penned%20by%20Atul%2C%20who%20had%20tragically%20lost%20his%20wife%20of%2036%20years%20to%20cancer%2C%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20Suhasini.%20Atul%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20showed%20how%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20his%20late%20wife%20happy%2C%20instead%20of%20%E2%80%9Csitting%20and%20crying%20over%20it%E2%80%9D.%20This%20resilient%20outlook%20towards%20life%20resonated%20with%20Suhasini%20and%20was%20instrumental%20in%20her%20falling%20in%20love%20with%20Atul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20lived%20alone%20in%20Mumbai%20for%2020%20years%20before%20meeting%20Atul%2C%20this%20is%20Suhasini%E2%80%99s%20first%20marriage.%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20thought%20of%20getting%20married.%20You%20commit%20because%20you%20want%20to%2C%20not%20because%20society%20is%20pushing%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707915442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FAjrqPGWSJgE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Remarriage%2C%20once%20taboo%2C%20is%20now%20embraced%2C%20exemplified%20by%20children%20advocating%20for%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20happiness.%20These%20Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20tales%20of%20love%20underscore%20the%20timeless%20strength%20of%20love%20and%20the%20need%20for%20companionship%20at%20all%20ages.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341793%2Fvalentines-day-love-stories-age-no-bar-senior-couples-remarriage-life-partners%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Ensures%20Ashok%20Chavan%20Will%20Be%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20From%20Maharashtra%2C%20Leaves%20Out%20Many%20of%20Its%20Own%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12132623%2FGFuyS5gaQAA6Ifj-1-e1707724634678.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20former%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Ashok%20Chavan%2C%20who%20had%20recently%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20was%20fielded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidates%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Chavan%20resigned%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20was%20widely%20expected%20that%20he%20would%20be%20given%20a%20national%20role%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20similar%20move%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Shinde)%2C%20led%20by%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20also%20fielded%20former%20Congress%20MP%20Milind%20Deora%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20poll.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeora%20had%20recently%20ended%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20decades-old%20association%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20joined%20the%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20which%20is%20perceived%20as%20the%20Deora%20family%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20political%20opponent%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20have%20become%20an%20opportunity%20for%20all%20parties%20to%20accommodate%20leaders%20in%20parliament%20well%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20new%20faces%20and%20some%20others%20are%20old%2C%20while%20some%20were%20rewarded%20for%20their%20significant%20organisational%20roles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20nominated%20multiple%20leaders%20from%20the%20Sangh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eparivar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20while%20regional%20parties%20rewarded%20some%20of%20their%20young%20faces%20who%20have%20remained%20loyal%20despite%20facing%20electoral%20losses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%20the%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20that%20the%20BJP%20released%2C%20nine%20Union%20ministers%20whose%20terms%20in%20the%20upper%20house%20were%20ending%20this%20April%20were%20absent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEducation%20minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%2C%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%2C%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20minister%20Narayan%20Rane%20and%20others%20like%20L.%20Murugan%20and%20Purushottam%20Rupala%20were%20missing%20from%20the%20list.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Murugan%20was%20nominated%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%2014)%2C%20while%20railways%2C%20communications%20and%20IT%20minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20filed%20his%20nomination%20from%20Odisha%20after%20the%20ruling%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20decided%20to%20support%20him%20again%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJunior%20IT%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20was%20not%20re-nominated%20from%20his%20Karnataka%20seat%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20instead%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fnarayansa-bandage-gets-bjp-ticket-for-rs-polls%2Farticle67835920.ece%5C%22%3Echoosing%20to%20field%20the%20Hindutva%20leader%20Narayana%20Bhandage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeculation%20is%20rife%20that%20most%20of%20the%20Union%20ministers%20who%20have%20not%20been%20re-nominated%20for%20the%20elections%20will%20now%20be%20fielded%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20whose%20term%20also%20ends%20in%20April%2C%20was%20re-nominated%20not%20from%20his%20home%20state%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20but%20from%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBarring%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%2C%20none%20of%20the%20nine%20outgoing%20BJP%20MPs%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20vacancies%20at%20ten%20seats%2C%20was%20renominated%2C%20which%20means%20leaders%20like%20Anil%20Jain%2C%20Anil%20Agarwal%20and%20G.V.L.%20Narsimha%20Rao%20will%20be%20given%20other%20roles%2C%20mostly%20in%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20accommodated%20former%20Congress%20leader%20R.P.N.%20Singh%2C%20another%20turncoat%20who%20switched%20camps%20in%202022%2C%20from%20its%20UP%20tally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20leaders%20were%20also%20nominated%20as%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rainbow%20social%20representation%20formula%20%E2%80%93%20Chaudhary%20Tejveer%20Singh%2C%20Sadhna%20Singh%2C%20Amarpal%20Maurya%2C%20Sangeeta%20Balwant%20and%20Naveen%20Jain%20are%20some%20of%20the%20leaders%20who%20will%20be%20representing%20UP%20for%20their%20party%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20renominated%20actress-politician%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20and%20fielded%20new%20faces%20like%20former%20bureaucrat-turned-party%20advisor%20Alok%20Ranjan%20and%20party%20leader%20and%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Ramji%20Lal%20Suman%20as%20its%20choices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20nomination%20of%20Bachchan%20and%20Ranjan%20has%20ruffled%20many%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20like%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%20and%20Pallavi%20Patel%2C%20who%20believe%20that%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20should%20have%20been%20used%20to%20nominate%20leaders%20from%20backward%20and%20Dalit%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20eastern%20India%2C%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20three%20seats%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20filled%20by%20the%20ruling%20BJD%E2%80%99s%20Debashish%20Samantray%2C%20a%20senior%20BJD%20leader%20who%20lost%20the%20last%20assembly%20polls%20but%20remained%20loyal%20to%20the%20party%20leadership%3B%20and%20young%20turk%20Subhasish%20Khuntia%20from%20Puri.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20third%20seat%20from%20the%20state%2C%20the%20BJD%20has%20extended%20its%20support%20to%20Vaishnaw%2C%20during%20whose%20tenure%20as%20Union%20railways%20minister%20the%20state%20received%20its%20highest-ever%20investment%20in%20rail%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitish-kumar-resigns-as-bihar-cm-expected-to-stake-claim-again-in-alliance-with-bjp%5C%22%3Ewhich%20recently%20joined%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%20(NDA)%2C%20has%20nominated%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20close%20aide%2C%20Sanjay%20Jha%2C%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20He%20will%20most%20likely%20win%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20has%20not%20been%20re-nominated%20and%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20he%20will%20be%20fielded%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%20six%20vacant%20seats%20from%20Bihar%2C%20three%20each%20are%20held%20by%20the%20NDA%20and%20by%20the%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFifty-six%20seats%20spread%20across%2015%20states%20will%20be%20filled%20up%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20February%2027.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20those%20retiring%20are%2028%20MPs%20from%20the%20BJP%3B%2011%20from%20the%20Congress%3B%20four%20from%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%3B%20four%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%3B%20two%20each%20from%20the%20BJD%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%3B%20and%20one%20each%20from%20the%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20Sikkim%20Democratic%20Front.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707914743000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12132623%2FGFuyS5gaQAA6Ifj-1-e1707724634678.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-ashok-chavan-rajya-sabha-milind-deora-shiv-sena-shinde%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20defector%2C%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20has%20been%20nominated%20by%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Shinde).%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20president%2C%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20is%20set%20to%20be%20a%20Gujarat%20MP%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-ashok-chavan-rajya-sabha-milind-deora-shiv-sena-shinde%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uber%20unveils%20%247%20bn%20stock%20buyback%20plan%20first%20for%20company%2C%20shares%20up%204.6%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707914430000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F14%2Ffull%2F1707913846-6499.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuber-unveils-7-bn-stock-buyback-plan-first-for-company-shares-up-4-6-124021401310_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20stock%20jumped%20about%204.6%25%20in%20premarket%20trading%20in%20New%20York.%20It%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20over%20the%20past%2012%20months%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuber-unveils-7-bn-stock-buyback-plan-first-for-company-shares-up-4-6-124021401310_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Fuber-unveils-7-bn-stock-buyback-plan-first-for-company-shares-up-4-6-124021401310_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus