0seat%20until%20his%20defeat%20to%20union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Amethi%20seat%20has%20been%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fgandhis-and-amethi-8899824%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENehru-Gandhi%20family%20since%20its%20formation%20in%201967%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ebarring%20a%20few%20years%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%201990s%20and%20in%20the%20latest%20stint%2C%20since%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20her%20move%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Gandhi%20has%20become%20the%20second%20member%20of%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%20to%20move%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%20following%20her%20mother-in-law%20and%20former%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20member%20the%20House%20from%201964%20to%201967%20before%20contesting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Raebareli.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Gandhi%20now%20vacating%20the%20Raebareli%20seat%2C%20there%20is%20speculation%20that%20her%20daughter%20Gandhi-Vadra%20might%20contest%20from%20the%20old%20Congress%20bastion%2C%20which%20has%20remained%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%20since%201952%20when%20Feroze%20Gandhi%20(Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20husband)%20won%20from%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESeven%20other%20candidates%20named%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Congress%20also%20named%20nine%20other%20candidates%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections.%20This%20includes%20sitting%20MP%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Akhilesh%20Prasad%20Singh%20from%20Bihar%2C%20Chandrakant%20Handore%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20Ajay%20Maken%2C%20Syed%20Naseer%20Hussain%2C%20G.C.%20Chandrashekhar%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20Ashok%20Singh%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Renuka%20Chowdhury%20and%20Anil%20Kumar%20Yadav%20from%20Telangana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESinghvi%20is%20the%20sitting%20Congress%20MP%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20but%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20this%20time%2C%20where%20the%20party%20is%20in%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%2C%20the%20state%20president%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Bihar%20is%20the%20other%20sitting%20MP%20and%20may%20require%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20and%20the%20Left%20to%20retain%20his%20seat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHandore%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20from%20Maharashtra%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20leaving%20the%20party%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20on%20Tuesday.%20Handore%20is%20at%20present%20the%20working%20president%20of%20the%20state%20unit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20treasurer%20Ajay%20Maken%20has%20been%20named%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20the%20party%20is%20in%20power%2C%20alongside%20sitting%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20Syed%20Naseer%20Hussain%20and%20G.C.%20Chandrashekhar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20where%20the%20party%20is%20also%20in%20power%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20named%20Renuka%20Chowdhury%20who%20will%20return%20to%20the%20house%20if%20elected%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20six%20years%2C%20along%20with%20Telangana%20youth%20Congress%20president%20Anil%20Kumar%20Yadav.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20there%20was%20speculation%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath%20of%20going%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%2C%20the%20party%20has%20named%20Ashok%20Singh%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20state%20unit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20total%20of%2056%20members%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%2015%20states%20are%20retiring%20in%20April%20and%20t