%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Yogendra%20Yadav%2C%20lightly%20edited%20for%20style%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElection%20season%20is%20here%20which%20means%20it%20is%20survey%20season.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20Today%20recently%20conducted%20a%20major%20survey%20and%20published%20it%20in%20the%20magazine%20with%20a%20bold%20headline%20which%20announced%20that%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%5D%20is%20going%20to%20win%20for%20the%20third%20time.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFriends%20called%20me%20up%20asking%20for%20my%20opinion%20on%20the%20survey.%20I%20said%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20predictions.%20I%20work%20to%20build%20the%20future%2C%20not%20to%20predict%20it.%20They%20still%20insisted%20that%20there%20must%20be%20something%20wrong%20and%20that%20it%20certainly%20is%20some%20stratagem%20of%20the%20government.%20But%20I%20do%20not%20agree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20way%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20survey%20is%20not%20to%20doubt%20its%20intentions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20involvement%20of%20money%20in%20it.%20Such%20games%20are%20involved%20no%20doubt.%20But%20if%20you%20want%20to%20understand%20any%20survey%2C%20you%20must%20delve%20deep%20into%20it%20and%20since%20it%20has%20been%20requested%20by%20so%20many%20friends%2C%20I%20will%20tell%20you%20five%20things%20to%20understand%20this%20survey%20and%20many%20such%20surveys%20that%20are%20yet%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComputer%20Assisted%20Telephonic%20Interviews%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20this%20survey%20is%20based%20on%20telephone%20interviews.%20It%20is%20not%20written%20anywhere.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20methodology%20note%20when%20you%20look%20at%20a%20survey.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20contains%20one%20word%20%E2%80%93%20CATI.%20What%20is%20CATI%3F%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20means%20this%20is%20based%20on%20Computer%20Assisted%20Telephonic%20Interviews.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20kind%20of%20surveys%20we%20used%20to%20conduct%20earlier%20involved%20our%20students%20or%20other%20people%20who%20would%20pay%20visits%20and%20knock%20on%20someone%E2%80%99s%20door%20and%20seek%20permission%20to%20speak.%20Then%20they%20would%20sit%20face%20to%20face%20and%20talk.%20Nothing%20like%20this%20has%20happened%20here.%20This%20has%20been%20done%20over%20the%20telephone.%20They%20got%20telephone%20numbers%20from%20as%20many%20companies%20as%20possible%20and%20called%20up%20people%20randomly.%20Then%20they%20spoke%20to%20those%20who%20responded.%20I%20am%20not%20pointing%20out%20any%20dishonesty%20in%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20has%20two%20consequences.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20one%20talks%20on%20the%20telephone.%20While%20replying%20to%20the%20person%20whom%20you%20cannot%20see%2C%20one%20would%20hesitate%20a%20bit%2C%20at%20least%20I%20would.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Esecond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20more%20important%20thing%20is%20%E2%80%93%20does%20everyone%20have%20a%20telephone%3F%20It%20is%20generally%20believed%20that%20nowadays%2C%20by%20and%20large%2C%20everyone%20walks%20around%20with%20a%20telephone.%20But%20look%20across%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NSS%20survey%20found%20two%20years%20ago%20that%2073%25%20households%20in%20the%20country%20had%20a%20telephone.%20Last%20year%2C%20CSDS%20conducted%20a%20survey%20on%20this%20issue%20and%20found%20that%2069%25%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20country%20possessed%20a%20telephone.%20That%20is%2C%20there%20are%20still%2031%25%20people%20who%20do%20not%20have%20a%20telephone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20type%20of%20such%20people%20is%20not%20very%20varied.%20Among%20the%20poorest%2C%2051%25%20do%20not%20possess%20a%20phone.%20Very%20few%20elderly%20people%20use%20phones.%20It%20means%20when%20you%20conduct%20telephonic%20interviews%2C%20you%20will%20not%20meet%20all%20types%20of%20people.%20Certain%20types%20of%20people%2C%20the%20bottom%2020%25-25%25%2C%20who%20do%20not%20have%20a%20telephone%2C%20will%20be%20left%20out%20of%20the%20survey.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20do%20all%20these%20people%20vote%20in%20the%20same%20way%3F%20Or%20are%20their%20political%20opinions%20the%20same%20as%20others%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CSDS%20had%20also%20checked%20this%20in%20its%20survey%20conducted%20last%20year.%20They%20observed%20that%20among%20those%20who%20had%20a%20telephone%2C%2041%25%20said%20they%20would%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20among%20those%20who%20did%20not%20have%20one%2C%2035%25%20said%20so.%20It%20means%20fewer%20people%20among%20those%20who%20are%20not%20included%20in%20this%20survey%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20telephone%20are%20going%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Read%20the%20survey%20carefully%20but%20remember%20that%20the%2020%25-25%25%20at%20the%20bottom%20are%20out%20of%20its%20purview.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20If%20you%20ask%2C%20they%20will%20say%20we%20have%20given%20weightage.%20I%20know%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20give%20weightage.%20But%20it%20is%20done%20when%20one%20has%20to%20adjust%2045%25%20to%2048%25.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20you%20give%20weightage.%20If%20you%20have%20left%20out%2025%25%20or%2030%25%20people%2C%20there%20is%20no%20way%20to%20fix%20it%20with%20weightage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMargin%20of%20error%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%20is%20margin%20of%20error.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20survey%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20an%20estimate.%20The%20estimate%20may%20be%20slightly%20lower%20or%20higher.%20The%20survey%20states%20how%20much%20can%20be%20adjusted.%20It%20is%20usually%20%C2%B12%25.%20It%20means%20that%20when%20the%20survey%20says%20that%20the%20NDA%20will%20get%2042%25%20votes%20and%20INDIA%20coalition%20will%20get%2037%25%20votes%20and%20there%20is%20an%20error%20of%20%C2%B12%25%20then%2042%20can%20be%2040%20and%2037%20can%20be%2039.%20You%20may%20think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20minute%20difference.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20minute.%20This%20little%20figure%20of%202%25%20votes%20can%20make%20a%20difference%20of%20at%20least%2040%20seats!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-rss-bjp-vhp-ram-temple%5C%22%3ERam%20Mandir%20wave%20and%20Ayodhya%20temple%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20everything%20that%20happened%2C%20this%20survey%20says%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20get%20304%20seats%2C%20that%20is%2C%20only%20one%20seat%20more%20than%20last%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20margin%20of%20error%20is%20-2%25%20then%20this%20figure%20can%20easily%20be%20264%20or%20260%20according%20to%20the%20estimate%20of%20this%20particular%20survey.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20this%20survey%20says%20that%20our%20estimate%20has%20a%20margin%20of%20error%20of%20%C2%B15%25%20at%20the%20local%2C%20or%20state%2C%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20survey%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20get%2042%25%20while%20the%20BJP%20will%20get%2053%25%20votes.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20%C2%B15%25%20error%2C%20then%20it%20can%20become%20a%20neck%20to%20neck%20fight%20with%2047%25%20or%2048%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20things%20might%20not%20be%20as%20they%20appear.%20You%20may%20say%20that%20the%20error%20may%20lie%20to%20the%20other%20side.%20True.%20But%20I%20am%20only%20urging%20you%20not%20to%20draw%20conclusions%20purely%20on%20this%20basis.%20Because%20the%20survey%20has%20a%20margin%20of%20error%20as%20every%20survey%20does.%20They%20have%20already%20told%20us.%20But%20remember%2C%20the%20vote%20has%20not%20been%20cast%20yet.%20Anyway%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20talk%20about%20it%20later.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDig%20deep%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20the%20third%20aspect.%20Let%20us%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20survey.%20When%20we%20usually%20view%20a%20survey%2C%20we%20only%20look%20at%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20and%20votes%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20about%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20need%20to%20give%20a%20thorough%20look%20and%20see%20what%20people%20say%20especially%20about%20the%20economy.%20Remember%20it%20does%20not%20include%20the%20bottom%2020%25.%20We%20still%20need%20to%20see%20what%20the%20top%2080%25%20are%20saying.%20They%20should%20be%20asked%20whether%20the%20employment%20situation%20in%20the%20country%20is%20worrisome.%20Yes%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20worrying.%2071%25%20people%20say%20that%20the%20condition%20is%20worrisome%20or%20very%20worrisome.%2054%25%20people%20say%20that%20it%20is%20very%20worrisome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20worrisome%20it%20is%2C%20but%20what%20did%20the%20Modi%20government%20do%20about%20it%3F%20Were%20the%20measures%20good%2C%20bad%20or%20satisfactory%3F%20Only%2032%25%20say%20that%20the%20government%20has%20done%20some%20decent%20work%20regarding%20unemployment.%2025%25%20say%20nothing%20much%20was%20done%20and%2031%25%20say%20nothing%20was%20done%20at%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmodi-amrit-kaal-hunger-unemployment%5C%22%3EHunger%20and%20Unemployment%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Amrit%20Kaal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20unemployment%20is%20a%20problem.%20Modi%20government%20is%20not%20doing%20anything.%20Ask%20them%20how%20much%20impact%20has%20inflation%20had%20on%20their%20household%E2%80%99s%20economy%20and%20financial%20condition.%2062%25%20people%20say%20that%20inflation%20has%20turned%20the%20situation%20so%20bad%20that%20the%20family%20is%20unable%20to%20survive.%20These%2062%25%20are%20not%20the%20bottom%205%25-10%25%20and%20bear%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20bottom%2020%25%20are%20still%20not%20included.%20Yet%20they%20are%20saying%20that%20survival%20is%20difficult.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEver%20since%20Modi%20ji%E2%80%99s%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20how%20has%20the%20financial%20condition%20of%20your%20family%20changed%3F%20Has%20it%20become%20better%20than%20before%3F%2035%25%20say%20that%20it%20has%20become%20worse%20than%20before%2C%2029%25%20say%20it%20is%20the%20same%20as%20before.%20If%20we%20add%20them%2C%20then%20two-thirds%20or%2064%25%20people%20are%20saying%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20improvement%20in%20their%20condition%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20not%20have%20happened%20till%20now%20but%20is%20there%20a%20possibility%20that%20there%20will%20be%20improvement%20in%20future%3F%20People%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20so%20either.%20Only%2025%25%20of%20the%20people%20believe%20that%20their%20situation%20will%20improve.%2030%25%20say%20it%20will%20get%20worse.%20The%20rest%20say%20it%20will%20remain%20the%20same.%20It%20means%20two-third%20people%20say%20that%20the%20situation%20would%20either%20remain%20the%20same%20or%20it%20would%20get%20worse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20if%20your%20condition%20is%20poor%2C%20whose%20condition%20is%20good%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20another%20question.%20That%20is%20why%20I%20say%20that%20one%20should%20always%20look%20inside%20the%20survey.%20You%20will%20get%20all%20the%20answers.%20They%20ask%20whether%20the%20work%20of%20this%20government%20has%20widened%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor.%20That%20the%20rich%20have%20become%20richer%3B%20the%20poor%20became%20poorer.%20Has%20this%20happened%3F%20Yes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E45%25%20agreed%20that%20it%20happened.%20Only%2037%25%20disagreed%2C%20which%20means%20more%20people%20are%20saying%20that%20the%20rich%20are%20getting%20richer%2C%20the%20poor%20are%20getting%20poorer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20a%20straightforward%20question%20is%20%E2%80%93%20who%20has%20benefited%20the%20most%20from%20the%20policies%20of%20this%20party%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E52%25%20people%20say%20big%20businesses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdani%20was%20not%20one%20of%20the%20options%20otherwise%20people%20would%20have%20picked%20it.%2052%25%20say%20only%20big%20people%20have%20benefitted%2C%20only%208%25-9%25%20say%20farmers%20have%20benefited%2C%206%25%20say%20labourers%20have%20benefited%2C%2015%25%20say%20others.%20But%20everyone%20else%20says%20that%20big%20people%20have%20benefited%20from%20the%20policies%20of%20this%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20look%2C%20this%20is%20the%20picture%20of%20the%20economic%20condition%20we%20are%20reiterating.%20The%20people%20in%20these%20surveys%20are%20not%20from%20the%20bottom%20strata.%20Even%20they%20are%20saying%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20very%20bad.%20The%20country%20is%20grappling%20with%20inflation%2C%20unemployment%20and%20the%20widening%20divide%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor.%20The%20question%20of%20vote%20is%20another%20matter.%20This%20is%20about%20the%20mood%20regarding%20economy%20which%20is%20very%20grim%20and%20negative.%20People%20are%20disappointed%20and%20angry.%20Now%2C%20let%20us%20move%20beyond%20the%20economic%20situation%20and%20look%20at%20the%20political%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20claims%20neither%20will%20he%20eat%20nor%20let%20anyone%20else%20eat%20(in%20terms%20of%20corruption).%20So%2C%20the%20survey%20asked%20people%20if%20corruption%20has%20reduced%20since%20this%20government%20was%20formed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20number%20of%20people%20who%20say%20that%20it%20reduced%20is%20equal%20to%20those%20who%20say%20it%20did%20not.%20So%2C%20this%20card%20does%20not%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20says%20that%20democracy%20is%20under%20threat.%20When%20the%20people%20were%20asked%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20democracy%20in%20the%20country%2C%2046%25%20people%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20threat%2C%2039%25%20said%20no%2C%20the%20rest%20had%20no%20opinion.%20It%20means%20they%20are%20talking%20about%20voting%20for%20the%20government%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20say%20that%20there%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20democracy.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20another%20related%20question%20%E2%80%93%20is%20the%20government%20misusing%20agencies%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnly%2037%25%20people%20say%20government%20not%20misusing%20ED%2C%20CBI%20to%20harass%20opposition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20agree%20with%20this%20too.%20In%20this%20case%20too%2C%2046%25%20people%20said%20yes%2C%20the%20government%20is%20using%20it%20unnecessarily%20and%20wrongfully%20to%20harass%20the%20opposition.%2037%25%20people%20disagreed.%20Now%2C%20remember%20that%20someone%20who%20is%20unable%20to%20say%20much%20openly%20will%20probably%20not%20express%20their%20views%20openly%20in%20the%20survey%20and%20will%20definitely%20not%20speak%20about%20it%20on%20the%20telephone.%20Yet%20when%20people%20were%20asked%20if%20they%20can%20express%20their%20views%20openly%20about%20politics%20and%20religion%20only%2047%25%20people%20claimed%20that%20they%20can%20do%20so%20on%20the%20phone%20while%2041%25%20people%20said%20on%20the%20phone%20that%20they%20cannot%20express%20their%20views%20openly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20fear%20and%20oppression%20in%20the%20country.%20There%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20democracy%20and%20there%20is%20no%20respite%20from%20corruption.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20are%20free%20to%20draw%20your%20own%20conclusion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-polls-verdicts-media-narratives-counting-day%5C%22%3EBackstory%3A%20Polls%2C%20Verdicts%20and%20Media%20Narratives%20on%20Counting%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETune%20out%20of%20toxic%20TV%20psephology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fifth%20and%20final%20point%3A%20As%20Ravish%20Kumar%20says%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20watch%20much%20TV%2C%20I%20too%20would%20advise%20you%20to%20watch%20surveys%20less.%20This%20country%20has%20more%20than%20enough%20psephologists.%20Everyone%2C%20from%20the%20person%20sitting%20at%20a%20paan%20shop%20to%20someone%20sitting%20in%20the%20park%2C%20is%20a%20psephologist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20I%20keep%20asking%20people%20to%20predict%20about%20things%20like%20the%20rain.%20What%20good%20is%20a%20prediction%20when%20it%20is%20about%20our%20own%20actions%2C%20something%20we%20are%20in%20control%20of%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20avoid%20psephology%2C%20watch%20less%20surveys.%20Remember%20that%20an%20election%20race%20is%20ahead%20but%20not%20even%20a%20single%20step%20has%20been%20taken%20yet.%20These%20surveys%20are%20merely%20an%20estimate%20of%20what%20a%20person%20is%20thinking%20of%20doing%20two%20and%20a%20half%20to%20three%20months%20from%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20a%20single%20person%20has%20cast%20their%20vote%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatever%20we%20want%2C%20will%20happen.%20There%20are%20challenges%2C%20but%20there%20are%20also%20possibilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20here%20are%20some%20verses%20by%20Sarveshwar%20Dayal%20Saxena.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20surrounded%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20by%20our%20disabilities%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20by%20possibilities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20wall%20can%20have%20doors%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20whole%20mountains%20can%20pass%20through%20each%20door.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20power%20is%20limited%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20powerlessness%20in%20everything%20too%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20arms%20are%20stunted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20the%20ocean%20has%20its%20limits%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStrength%20is%20just%20another%20name%20for%20desire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20land%20between%20life%20and%20death%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoes%20not%20belong%20to%20destiny%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20to%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20look%20at%20the%20mood%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20spoil%20your%20own%20mood.%20Move%20forward%20and%20do%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FDbpjBwivhmE%3Fsi%3DC7QawxF7VIGG1DEM%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETranslated%20and%20transcribed%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707906895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fhow-to-cut-through-the-fog-in-election-surveys%22%2C%22su