0arrest%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20took%20cognizance%20of%20the%20chargesheet%20filed%20against%20him%20under%20FIR59%2F2020%2C%20along%20with%20JNU%20scholar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsharjeel-imam-jail-uapa-activist-civil-society-support%5C%22%3ESharjeel%20Imam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20conspiring%20and%20instigating%20the%20riots%20that%20took%20place%20in%20February%20that%20year%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20October%202020%2C%20Khalid%20was%20also%20charged%20under%20FIR%20101%2F2020%20that%20related%20to%20vandalism%20and%20arson%20during%20the%20riots%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fumar-khalid-delhi-court-khajuri-khas-riots-aarogya-setu%5C%22%3EKhajuri%20Khas%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202021%2C%20Khalid%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20a%20sessions%20court%20in%20Delhi%2C%20filed%20under%20FIR%20101%2F2020%2C%20but%20continued%20to%20be%20incarcerated%20due%20to%20the%20charges%20against%20him%20under%20FIR%2059%2F2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20FIR%2059%2F2020%2C%20Khalid%20has%20been%20charged%20for%20various%20offences%2C%20including%20rioting%2C%20murder%20and%20unlawful%20assembly%20as%20well%20as%20sections%20of%20the%20UAPA%20and%20the%20Arms%20Act%2C%201959.%20He%20is%20also%20facing%20charges%20under%20sedition%2C%20and%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20eight%20months%20of%20hearings%2C%20in%20March%202022%2C%20a%20Delhi%20sessions%20court%20denied%20him%20bail.%20Khalid%20appealed%20this%20decision%20in%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20the%20following%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20subsequently%20ordered%20that%20the%20bail%20plea%20be%20heard%20regularly%20from%20May%2023%2C%20so%20that%20the%20hearings%20close%20before%20the%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20breaks%20for%20summer%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearings%20were%20then%20adjourned%20on%20June%204%2C%202022%2C%20as%20the%20court%20went%20for%20summer%20vacation%20till%20July%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2018%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20rejected%20his%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20on%20November%2018%2C%20Khalid%20moved%20the%20Karkardooma%20court%20seeking%20a%20two-week%20interim%20bail%20to%20attend%20his%20sister%E2%80%99s%20marriage%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%203%2C%202022%20the%20Karkardooma%20court%20acquitted%20Khalid%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98stone%20pelting%E2%80%99%20case%20related%20to%20the%20Delhi%20riots%2C%20but%20continued%20to%20detain%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98larger%20conspiracy%E2%80%99%20around%20the%20riots.%20On%20December%2012%20of%20that%20year%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-umar-khalid-granted-interim-bail-to-attend-sisters-wedding%5C%22%3Ewas%20granted%3C%2Fa%3E%20interim%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fumar-khalid-the-historian-his-continued-imprisonment-is-a-loss-to-the-academic-world%5C%22%3EUmar%20Khalid%2C%20the%20Historian%3A%20His%20Continued%20Imprisonment%20Is%20a%20Loss%20to%20the%20Academic%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%206%2C%202023%2C%20Khalid%20filed%20a%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20appealing%20against%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20October%202022%20order%2C%20denying%20him%20bail%2C%20which%20he%20has%20now%20withdrawn%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2018%2C%202023%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%2C%20comprising%20Justices%20A.S.%20Bopanna%20and%20Hima%20Kohli%2C%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20sought%20a%20response%20to%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20petition%20within%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20then%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea%20has%20been%20rescheduled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fjournal%2Fumar-khalid-bail-application-tracker%2F%5C%22%3E14%3C%2Fa%3E%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707901886000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F18112637%2FUmar-Khalid.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fumar-khalid-withdraws-bail-plea-in-supreme-court-citing-change-of-circumstances%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Khalid%2C%20who%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20September%202020%2C%20through%20his%20lawyer%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20said%20that%20he%20will%20%E2%80%98try%20his%20luck%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20lower%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fumar-khalid-withdraws-bail-plea-in-supreme-court-citing-change-of-circumstances%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Agenda%20Is%20to%20Silence%20Us'%3A%20Key%20Social%20Media%20Accounts%20Withheld%2C%20Farmers%20Vow%20to%20Boycott%20Centre's%20Meetings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14132746%2FUntitled-design-7-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Over%20a%20dozen%20accounts%20on%20X%20and%20Facebook%20which%20functioned%20as%20official%20pages%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20organisations%20and%20unions%20ahead%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20have%20been%20withheld%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20ostensibly%20upon%20government%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20was%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20farmers%20were%20withheld%20a%20day%20before%20they%20were%20to%20start%20their%20protest%2C%20on%20February%2013.%20The%20call%20for%20protest%20was%20jointly%20given%20by%20Sanyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-political)%20led%20by%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20and%20Kisan%20Majdoor%20Morcha%20co-ordinator%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-internet-haryana-twitter-accounts%5C%22%3Eban%20on%20their%20social%20media%20accounts%20and%20an%20extended%20internet%20ban%20in%20seven%20districts%20of%20Haryana%3C%2Fa%3E%20till%20February%2015%2C%20the%20Haryana%20police%20has%20banned%20the%20entry%20of%20farmers%20through%20multi-layered%20blockades%20on%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Shambhu%20border%20from%20Patiala%20side%20and%20Khanauri%20border%20from%20Sangrur%20district%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20spent%20February%2013%20night%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border.%20There%20was%20heavy%20deployment%20of%20paramilitary%20forces%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20border%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20stopping%20them%20from%20crossing%20over%20to%20Haryana%2C%20the%20Haryana%20police%20fired%20pellets%20at%20and%20used%20drones%20to%20teargas%20protesting%20farmers%20leading%20to%20injuries%20and%20chaos%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border.%20As%20per%20reports%2C%20over%20100%20farmers%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20media%20accounts%20withheld%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20accounts%20and%20Facebook%20pages%20of%20prominent%20farmer%20leaders%20like%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20the%20coordinator%20of%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20BKU%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20Mann%2C%20Surjit%20Singh%20Phull%20from%20BKU%20Krantikari%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Harpal%20Sangha%2C%20Ashok%20Danoda%20from%20Haryana%20and%20many%20others%20have%20been%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20banned%20official%20pages%20which%20supported%20the%20movement%20and%20posted%20updates%20on%20it%2C%20like%20%40Tractor2twitr_P%20run%20by%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20and%20Progressive%20Farmers%20Front%2C%20run%20by%20Guramneet%20Singh%20Mangat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBKU%20(SBS)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20farmer%20unions%20which%20was%20leading%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20from%20Ambala%2C%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Gaon%20Sawera%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20page%20run%20by%20independent%20journalist%20Mandeep%20Punia%20has%20been%20withheld%2C%20as%20has%20been%20Mandeep%E2%80%99s%20personal%20page.%20Mandeep%20is%20a%20prominent%20name%20supporting%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20and%20had%20been%20arrested%20in%202020.%20In%20the%20jail%2C%20Mandeep%20took%20notes%20on%20his%20legs%20and%20then%20wrote%20a%20report%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Caravan.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20withholding%20these%20accounts%20has%20been%20largely%20understood%20to%20be%20opaque.%20Guramneet%E2%80%99s%20personal%20X%20account%20is%20still%20up%2C%20as%20is%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%E2%80%99s%20X%20account.%20But%20Dallewal%E2%80%99s%20Facebook%20page%20is%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accounts%20received%20a%20message%20from%20X%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CYour%20account%20has%20been%20withheld%20in%20IN%20%5BIndia%5D%20in%20response%20to%20a%20legal%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20official%20page%20of%20Kisan%20Majdoor%20Morcha%2C%20which%20was%20started%20recently%20ahead%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20protest%2C%20is%20still%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20earlier%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202020-2021%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20banned%20many%20social%20media%20accounts%20including%20the%20official%20page%20of%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%2C%20which%20largely%20functioned%20as%20the%20digital%20outpost%20of%20the%20SKM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20then%20high%20profile%20supporters%20like%20Punjabi%20singer%20Jazzy%20B%20and%20Khalsa%20Aid%E2%80%99s%20Ravi%20Singh%2C%20along%20with%20independent%20journalist%20Sandeep%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20had%20been%20withheld%20and%20continue%20to%20be%20under%20lock%20and%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccounts%20meant%20to%20debunk%20propaganda%20targeted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20running%20the%20%40Tractor2Twitr_i%20page%20on%20X%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20withheld%20in%20the%20time%20between%20he%20spoke%20and%20this%20report%20was%20published%20%E2%80%93%20said%20that%20all%20these%20accounts%20were%20withheld%20as%20farmer%20leaders%20were%20sitting%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20union%20ministers%20on%20February%2012.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20an%20assumption%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Union%20government%20but%20the%20Punjab%20government%20too%20which%20was%20involved%20in%20singling%20out%20farmer%20union%20leaders%E2%80%99%20accounts.%20This%20is%20a%20dangerous%20trend%2C%20as%20those%20accounts%20which%20were%20running%20propaganda%20against%20farmers%20are%20getting%20support%20while%20the%20official%20mouthpieces%20of%20farmers%20meant%20to%20debunk%20the%20propaganda%20and%20misinformation%20are%20being%20targeted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavjit%20said%20that%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202024%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cagenda%20is%20to%20silence%20all%20those%20who%20dare%20to%20speak%20against%20or%20question%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20as%20it%20will%20affect%20his%20image.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Meeting%20only%20if%20social%20media%20accounts%20restored%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavjit%20said%20that%20the%20leaders%20had%20decided%20to%20boycott%20further%20meetings%20till%20the%20accounts%20are%20restored.%20%E2%80%9CFarmer%20union%20leaders%20have%20decided%20that%20the%20invitation%20for%20a%20third%20round%20of%20meetings%20will%20be%20accepted%20only%20if%20the%20government%20restarts%20these%20social%20media%20accounts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20leader%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20Mann%20also%20shared%20that%20he%20was%20attending%20the%20farmers%20and%20union%20ministers%E2%80%99%20meeting%20on%20February%2012%20night%2C%20when%20he%20got%20a%20message%20on%20WhatsApp%20that%20his%20X%20account%20had%20been%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20showed%20the%20message%20to%20union%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20but%20he%20feigned%20ignorance%20and%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20this%20action.%20I%20asked%20Piyush%20Goyal%20how%20his%20government%20could%20ask%20us%20to%20believe%20them.%20I%20also%20asked%20Punjab%20NRI%20affairs%20minister%20Kuldeep%20Singh%20Dhaliwal%20who%20was%20representing%20the%20Punjab%20government%20if%20it%20was%20the%20AAP%20government%20who%20was%20getting%20our%20social%20media%20accounts%20blocked%20but%20he%20too%20refused%20to%20answer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamandeep%20said%20that%20this%20is%20a%20clear%20attempt%20to%20exert%20pressure%20on%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20afraid%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20strength%2C%20which%20they%20have%20already%20seen%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202020.%20Let%20them%20try%20whatever%20they%20want%20to%2C%20farmers%20are%20united%20and%20committed%20to%20their%20cause%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20spoke%20to%20Harinder%20Happy%2C%20a%20PhD%20student%20from%20JawaharLal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Delhi%20who%2C%20among%20others%2C%20was%20running%20the%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%2C%20the%20official%20Twitter%20page%20of%20the%20SKM%20last%20time.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20resorted%20to%20these%20tactics%20last%20time%20too%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20two%20years%20since%20they%20banned%20the%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%20page%2C%20which%20had%20over%20five%20lakh%20followers.%20Our%20page%20was%20withheld%20when%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20was%20at%20its%20peak.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20considering%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%202024%20and%20the%20mass%20support%20for%20farmers%2C%20they%20withheld%20the%20X%20accounts%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day%20of%20the%20protest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20highlighted%20how%20%E2%80%9Con%20one%20hand%2C%20BJP%20is%20giving%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20they%20were%20not%20implementing%20their%20findings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707901810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14132746%2FUntitled-design-7-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20now%20running%20the%20%40Tractor2Twitr_i%20page%20on%20X%20said%20that%20these%20accounts%20were%20withheld%20as%20farmer%20leaders%20were%20sitting%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20union%20ministers%20on%20February%2012.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20warship%20destroyed%20off%20Crimean%20coast%2C%20Ukraine%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707898620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-ukraine-black-sea_6455027.png%3F20240214084709%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frussian-warship-destroyed-off-crimean-coast-ukraine-says-13071286%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20forces%20destroyed%20a%20Russian%20warship%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Crimea%2C%20Ukraine's%20military%20