ure%20or%20fungus%20will%20set%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20cautions%20Vaibhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F272981%2Fhow-to-grow-vegetables-in-pots-terrace-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESorting%20out%20the%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20ordeal.%20They%20need%20to%20be%20checked%20by%20hand%20and%20smelled%20to%20catch%20any%20rot%20that%20has%20set%20in.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20one%20seed%20with%20fungus%20can%20affect%20the%20whole%20batch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20warns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%203%3A%20Divide%20the%20batch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESorting%20through%20the%20seeds%20leaves%20you%20with%20the%20good%20ones%20and%20the%20bad.%20You%20discard%20the%20bad%20ones%20and%20proceed%20with%20silvering%20the%20good%20ones.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20step%2C%20the%20tail-like%20portion%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20seed%20is%20cut%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vaibhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270107%2Fterrace-gardening-tips-how-to-grow-vegetables-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20then%20divided%20into%20two%20batches.%20%E2%80%9COne%20batch%20is%20put%20into%20soil%20trays%20and%20the%20other%20in%20wooden%20trays%20on%20slotted%20angle%20racks.%20Both%20the%20setups%20are%20kept%20in%20a%20room%20where%20the%20temperature%20is%20stringently%20controlled.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-2-1707479222.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20saffron%20threads%20are%20the%20stigma%20of%20the%20flower%20that%20are%20harvested%20and%20dried%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3