%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20patented%20bamboo%20chair%20was%20made%20by%20Professor%20Ankit%20Kumar%20Changawala%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339622%2Frare-species-of-bamboo-in-kerala-india-farming-for-sustainable-future-desertification%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduction%20to%20bamboo%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20his%20idea%20of%20a%20bamboo%20chair%2C%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20attend%20a%20workshop%20in%202019%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20World%20Bamboo%20Workshop%20was%20the%20first%20symposium%20in%20India%20focused%20on%20bamboo%20and%20its%20uses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20symposium%20profoundly%20changed%20Ankit%E2%80%99s%20perception%20of%20bamboo.%20Previously%2C%20there%20was%20merely%20abundant%20vegetation%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20see%20its%20untapped%20potential%20and%20how%20it%20was%20being%20wasted.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20community%20of%20bamboo%20artisans%20whose%20craft%20was%20fading%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Kotwaliyas%20in%20the%20region%20are%20renowned%20for%20their%20skill%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20their%20art%20was%20being%20neglected%20and%20dying%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20also%20began%20educating%20his%20students%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20using%20Bambusa%20bamboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20educating%20more%20people%20and%20reaching%20out%20to%20craftsmen%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20disrupting%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20period%2C%20Ankit%20encountered%20craftsmen%20suffering%20due%20to%20the%20decline%20in%20tourism.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learned%20that%20the%20younger%20generations%20of%20these%20craftsmen%20were%20reluctant%20to%20continue%20the%20tradition%20as%20they%20saw%20no%20future%20in%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Ankit%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20immense%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334214%2Fmaharashtra-tetwali-village-namita-namdev-bhurkood-bamboo-kandils-trains-tribal-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20of%20bamboo%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20crucial.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20them%20to%20abandon%20their%20craft%20and%20migrate%20to%20cities%20in%20search%20of%20jobs.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20create%20daily-use%20furniture%20with%20modern%20designs%20to%20appeal%20to%20urban%20consumers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Ankit%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20students%20and%20four%20local%20craftsmen%2C%20embarked%20on%20creating%20sustainable%20yet%20modern%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESturdy%2C%20Sustainable%20and%20Modern%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20for%20Ankit%20was%20to%20understand%20the%20bamboo.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20designers%2C%20we%20work%20with%20measurements%20but%20these%20traditional%20craftsmen%20have%20their%20own%20way%20of%20working.%20We%20realised%20how%20the%20wood%20in%20bamboo%20towards%20the%20lower%20end%20was%20stronger%20and%20thicker%20than%20the%20upper%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20took%20almost%20two%20years%20for%20Ankit%20to%20design%20and%20built%20the%20chair.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-7-1707399921-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341210%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20took%20almost%20two%20years%20for%20Ankit%20to%20design%20and%20build%20the%20chair.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20craftsmen%20comfortable%20and%20win%20their%20confidence%2C%20Ankit%20took%20his%20designs%20to%20their%20workshops.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20make%20them%20feel%20comfortable%20and%20work%20as%20a%20team.%20They%20were%20at%20their%20best%20form%20when%20they%20were%20using%20their%20own%20traditional%20machines%20and%20materials.%20I%20used%20to%20visit%20their%20workshops%20in%20order%20to%20work%20on%20the%20chair%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Bambusa%20bamboo%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20chose%20Bambusa%20because%20it%20has%20a%20great%20load-bearing%20capacity.%20It%20is%20long-lasting%20and%20sturdy%20enough%20to%20be%20used%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20The%20knots%20in%20the%20variety%20are%20very%20close%20making%20it%20very%20strong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20variety%20is%20also%20abundantly%20available%20in%20the%20area.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20companies%20making%20furniture%20from%20bamboo%20imported%20from%20different%20countries.%20If%20you%20go%20online%20and%20try%20to%20find%20a%20simple%20piece%20of%20furniture%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo%2C%20it%20will%20be%20quite%20expensive.%20The%20reason%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20because%20they%20are%20not%20using%20Indian%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20adds%20that%20he%20used%20a%20native%20variety%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20chair%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffordable%20and%20cheap.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20point%20in%20making%20a%20product%20that%20the%20masses%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford.%20It%20defeats%20the%20entire%20sustainability%20angle%20behind%20the%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CGujarat%20government%20has%20also%20released%20a%20lot%20of%20schemes%20for%20the%20farmers%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20grow%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20funding%20the%20project%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20it%20out%20of%20my%20own%20pocket.%20I%20knew%20if%20I%20had%20gone%20out%20looking%20for%20funding%20then%20this%20would%20not%20have%20happened.%20Investors%20would%20lack%20confidence%20in%20the%20idea%20since%20it%20was%20new%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Ankit%20nearly%20two%20years%20to%20complete%20the%20design%20and%20make%20the%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20get%20the%20chair%20patented.%20The%20main%20reason%20behind%20it%20was%20to%20showcase%20the%20potential%20of%20native%20bamboo%20species%20to%20the%20world.%20Once%20my%20design%20got%20patented%2C%20it%20generated%20a%20conversation%20among%20people%20about%20the%20potential%20of%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20chair%20can%20endure%20150%20kgs%20of%20weight%20and%20can%20last%20more%20than%2020%20years.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341211%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20chair%20can%20endure%20150%20kg%20of%20weight%20and%20can%20last%20more%20than%2020%20years.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20chair%2C%20Ankit%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20polish%20on%20the%20chair%20is%20done%20using%20natural%20oils.%20It%20can%20endure%20weights%20of%20more%20than%20150%20kg%2C%20and%20the%20furniture%20has%20also%20been%20treated%20to%20protect%20against%20any%20kind%20of%20insects.%20The%20life%20of%20the%20chair%20is%20up%20to%2020%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20does%20not%20want%20to%20commercialise%20the%20chair.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20received%20numerous%20inquiries%20about%20whether%20I%20am%20selling%20these%20chairs.%20However%2C%20my%20goal%20is%20not%20profit%20or%20loss.%20My%20aim%20is%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20provide%20training%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20working%20on%20a%20proposal%20to%20present%20to%20my%20university%20to%20initiate%20a%20program%20where%20individuals%20can%20come%20and%20learn%20how%20to%20make%20chairs%20and%20collaborate%20with%20me%20to%20create%20more%20furniture.%20This%20approach%20will%20allow%20me%20to%20train%20craftsmen%20in%20producing%20sustainable%20yet%20modern%20furniture%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20view%20Ankit%E2%80%99s%20patent%2C%20visit%20this%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsearch.ipindia.gov.in%2FDesignQRStatus%2FPDF_Viewer.aspx%3FAppNo%3DMzk1MTU0LTAwMQ%3D%3D%26CNo%3DMTQ5NTI0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Elink%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20Ankit%2C%20You%20can%20reach%20him%20at%209879262737%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Ankit)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707402725000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-6-1707399873.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341205%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ankit%20Kumar%20Changawala%20from%20Veer%20Narmad%20South%20Gujarat%20University%2C%20recently%20patented%20a%20chair%20crafted%20from%20Bambusa%20bamboo%2C%20a%20locally%20abundant%20variety%20of%20South%20Gujarat%2C%20to%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20bamboo%20in%20furniture%20making.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bhumi%20Pednekar%E2%80%99s%20Bhakshak%3A%20How%20A%20TISS%20Team%20Blew%20The%20Lid%20Off%20Bihar%20Shelter%20Home%20Abuse%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20trailer%20for%20%E2%80%98Bhakshak%E2%80%99%20opens%20with%20a%20poignant%20scene%20depicting%20young%20girls%20residing%20in%20a%20shelter%20home%20in%20Bihar.%20Starring%20Bhumi%20Pednekar%2C%20Aditya%20Srivastava%2C%20and%20Sanjay%20Mishra%2C%20the%20film%20delves%20into%20the%20harrowing%20narrative%20inspired%20by%20the%20Muzaffarpur%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308756%2Fmanila-bachan-recovery-journey-from-sexual-abuse-bipolar-disorder-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshelter%20home%20abuse%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20reverberated%20across%20the%20nation%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Bihar%20MLA%20Brajesh%20Thakur%20and%2011%20others%20currently%20serve%20a%20life%20sentence%20for%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20appalling%20sexual%20assault%20of%20numerous%20minor%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20tragic%20episode%20came%20to%20light%20through%20a%20social%20audit%20report%20conducted%20by%20a%20dedicated%20team%20of%20researchers%20from%20Koshish%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Field%20Action%20Project%20focusing%20on%20homelessness%20and%20destitution%20at%20the%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20(TISS).%20Over%20a%20span%20of%20six%20months%2C%20commencing%20in%20October%202017%2C%20a%20team%20of%20seven%20diligently%20surveyed%20more%20than%20110%20institutions%20either%20operated%20or%20supported%20by%20the%20Bihar%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20primary%20aim%20of%20the%20social%20audit%20was%20to%20assess%20the%20functioning%20of%20these%20institutions%2C%20gauge%20the%20well-being%20of%20their%20residents%2C%20and%20identify%20gaps%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20care%20provided%2C%20the%20findings%20were%20nothing%20short%20of%20alarming%20for%20the%20researchers.%20They%20uncovered%20widespread%20instances%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20and%20violence%20in%20nearly%2017%20institutions%2C%20revealing%20a%20deeply%20disturbing%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20submitted%20by%20TISS%20to%20the%20Bihar%20Government%20in%20May%202018%20marked%2017%20institutions%20as%20%E2%80%98grave%20concern%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20required%20immediate%20attention.%20One%20of%20these%20institutions%20was%20Balika%20Grih%20(girl%E2%80%99s%20shelter%20home)%20run%20by%20Brajesh%20Thakur%E2%80%99s%20NGO%20Seva%20Sankalp%20Evam%20Vikas%20Samiti.%20The%20TISS%20researchers%2C%20led%20by%20Mohd%20Tarique%2C%20found%20that%20the%20girls%20in%20this%20home%20were%20sexually%20abused%20and%20assaulted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20investigation%20by%20the%20police%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313961%2Flawyer-helps-child-sexual-abuse-victims-win-compensation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedical%20examination%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2034%20girls%20at%20the%20home%2C%20between%20the%20ages%20of%207%20and%2017%2C%20were%20sexually%20assaulted.%20The%20case%20was%20then%20transferred%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%2020%20people%20were%20charged%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20accused%2C%20Thakur%2C%20who%20ran%20other%20shelter%20homes%20too%2C%20was%20convicted%20on%20multiple%20grounds%20of%20rape%2C%20gangrape%20(Section%20376(d)%2C%20IPC)%2C%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20aggravated%20sexual%20assault%20under%20Section%206%20of%20the%20POCSO%20Act%2C%20and%20offences%20under%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20Mohd%20Tarique%20about%20how%20the%20TISS%20unearthed%20this%20heinous%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20social%20audit%20that%20exposed%20an%20appalling%20case%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fshutterstock_259928615_11zon-1707462732-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Representational%20image%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fshutterstock_259928615_11zon-1707462732-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2