ay%20homes%20for%20women%2C%20old%20age%20homes%2C%20and%20more.%20Initially%2C%20only%20institutions%20run%20by%20NGOs%20were%20to%20be%20covered%2C%20but%20later%20Government-run%20homes%20were%20also%20included%20in%20the%20ambit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20really%20helped%20the%20team%2C%20according%20to%20Tarique%2C%20was%20the%20methodology%20they%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20worked%20with%20the%20homeless%20for%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20I%20knew%20how%20we%20needed%20to%20approach%20and%20speak%20to%20the%20residents%20of%20such%20homes.%20We%20had%20strict%20rules%20when%20we%20entered%20each%20institution%20and%20spoke%20separately%20to%20the%20chiefs%2C%20staff%20members%2C%20and%20residents%2C%20and%20conducted%20a%20physical%20check%20of%20each%20facility%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Tarique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20from%20the%20time%20they%20entered%20a%20home%2C%20they%20looked%20for%20non-verbal%20signs%2C%20which%20said%20more%20than%20words.%20They%20gauged%20the%20situation%20from%20the%20atmosphere%20at%20each%20institution.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20they%20found%20children%20sitting%20very%20quietly%2C%20in%20an%20organised%20manner%2C%20with%20fear%20in%20their%20eyes%2C%20it%20was%20a%20red%20flag%2C%20says%20Tarique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20did%20not%20allow%20any%20staff%20members%20to%20join%20when%20they%20conducted%20focus%20groups%20with%20the%20residents%2C%20be%20they%20children%20or%20elders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20win%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20children%20in%20a%20short%20period%20of%20time.%20We%20did%20not%20allow%20any%20staff%20members%20inside%20when%20we%20spoke.%20We%20did%20not%20accept%20any%20refreshments%20when%20we%20entered.%20In%20fact%2C%20if%20staff%20members%20tried%20to%20delay%20our%20meeting%20with%20the%20residents%20by%20offering%20snacks%2C%20it%20was%20also%20a%20sign%20of%20something%20amiss%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Tarique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20staff%20tried%20to%20keep%20interrupting%20in%20the%20pretext%20of%20some%20refreshments%20while%20they%20spoke%20to%20the%20residents%2C%20that%20too%20was%20a%20sign%20of%20alarm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20thing%2C%20according%20to%20the%20social%20worker%2C%20was%20not%20acting%20immediately%2C%20based%20on%20the%20concerns.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20the%20child%20will%20test%20you%20by%20sharing%20a%20minor%20incident.%20If%20you%20go%20and%20question%20the%20staff%20immediately%2C%20the%20child%20will%20be%20reprimanded%20and%20won%E2%80%99t%20trust%20you.%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20when%20they%20trust%20you%20that%20they%20will%20feel%20comfortable%20sharing%20the%20graver%20incident.%20If%20we%20get%20into%20the%20mode%20of%20fixing%20things%2C%20we%20might%20lose%20out%20on%20the%20more%20serious%20incident%20that%20the%20child%20wanted%20to%20report%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20adopted%20a%20balanced%2C%20strategic%20approach%2C%20where%20being%20neutral%20was%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20seldom%20share%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340517%2Fmansi-poddar-psychologist-therapist-childhood-abuse-trauma-molestation-domestic-violence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincidents%20of%20abuse%3C%2Fa%3E%20openly%2C%20according%20to%20him.%20They%20tried%20to%20create%20an%20environment%20that%20encouraged%20children%20to%20come%20forward%20and%20speak.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20shared%20that%20another%20child%20has%20been%20abused.%20They%20will%20always%20use%20another%20person%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20conducted%20focus%20groups%2C%20children%20who%20wished%20to%20speak%20alone%20did%20so.%20It%20was%20through%20this%20approach%20that%20they%20found%20alarming%20signs%20at%20the%20Balika%20Grih%20in%20Muzaffarpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20observed%20the%20non-verbal%20communication%20between%20the%20staff%20members.%20At%20these%20places%20that%20they%20marked%20%E2%80%98grave%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20found%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20and%20the%20air%20of%20something%20being%20hidden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20over%20six-month%20audit%20across%2038%20districts%2C%20they%20finally%20submitted%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20dreadful%20situation%20at%20the%20Balika%20Gruh%2C%20which%20was%20a%20state-run%20home%2C%20they%20found%20that%20it%20was%20being%20run%20in%20a%20questionable%20manner.%20They%20also%20found%20that%20the%20girls%20were%20locked%20up%20in%20their%20rooms%20and%20had%20no%20access%20to%20open%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20escalated%20their%20fears%20and%20recommended%20immediate%20further%20probe.%20The%20Bihar%20Police%20then%20filed%20an%20FIR%20at%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20police%20station%20in%20Muzaffarpur%20in%20May%202018%20and%20named%2011%20people%2C%20including%20Brajesh%20Thakur.%20A%20medical%20report%20found%20that%20%E2%80%9C34%20of%20the%2044%20girls%20at%20the%20home%20were%20drugged%20and%20raped%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20intervened%20and%20transferred%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20charged%2020%20people%2C%20including%20nine%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girls%20were%20shifted%20to%20different%20homes%20soon%20and%2017%20of%20them%20were%20sent%20to%20Bengaluru%20to%20do%20hotel%20management.%20A%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20found%20that%2017%20of%20those%2034%20girls%20have%20built%20their%20lives%20and%20are%20working%20in%20hotels%20across%20the%20country.%20Seventeen%20of%20the%20girls%20are%20with%20their%20families%20now%2C%20as%20per%20the%20same%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20like%20we%20are%20born%20again%2C%20in%20a%20better%20world.%20We%20have%20a%20reason%20to%20put%20our%20torturous%20past%20behind%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20woman%20from%20the%20home%20who%20works%20in%20a%20four-star%20hotel%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fpatna%2Fjobs-in-hospitality-girls-who-faced-abuse-in-muzaffarpur-shelter-home-shed-past-9041329%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Five%20years%20on%2C%20girls%20who%20survived%20abuse%20in%20Muzaffarpur%20shelter%20home%20rebuild%20their%20lives%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Santosh%20Singh%20for%20The%20Indian%20Express%2C%20Published%20in%2025%20November%2C%202023%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707401110000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fshutterstock_259928615_11zon-1707462732-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20movie%20Bhakshak%20is%20based%20on%20the%20harrowing%20Muzaffarpur%20girls'%20shelter%20home%20case%2C%20where%2034%20minors%20endured%20sexual%20abuse%20%E2%80%94%20discovered%20during%20a%20TISS%20social%20audit%20in%202018.%20The%20film%20depicts%20the%20distressing%20narrative%20of%20this%20case%2C%20revealing%20systemic%20sexual%20abuse%20in%20many%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20institutions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Visiting%20Rajasthan%20in%20Winter%3F%20This%20Unique%20Mud%20Homestay%20Is%20Run%20by%20a%20Family%20of%20Durrie%20Weavers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20year%202009%2C%20a%20couple%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20Brad%20and%20Lucy%2C%20were%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20the%20final%20leg%20of%20their%20Rajasthan%20trip.%20The%20fabled%20city%20of%20Jodhpur%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333558%2Fbest-farm-stays-in-india-with-natural-pool-organic-food-slow-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20destination%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20choice.%20Armed%20with%20postcards%20that%20boasted%20the%20magnificent%20forts%20and%20camera%20pictures%20that%20showed%20off%20the%20colourful%20%3Cem%3Ebazaars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20ready%20for%20more%20such%20authentic%20Rajasthani%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20stay%20in%20a%20Rajasthani%20home%20would%20be%20the%20icing%20on%20the%20cake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20place%20they%20came%20across%20in%20Jodhpur%20was%20the%20village%20of%20Salawas%20which%20prides%20itself%20on%20the%20legendary%20%3Cem%3Edhurrie%3C%2Fem%3E%20making%20(handwoven%20floor%20coverings%20whose%20designs%20are%20inspired%20by%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20culture).%20Lucy%20could%20hardly%20contain%20her%20excitement%20on%20meeting%20Pukhraj%20ji%E2%80%99s%20family%20whose%20ancestors%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20the%20artisanal%20craft%20for%20over%20seven%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20her%20arms%20were%20loaded%20with%20purchases%20of%20woven%20%3Cem%3Edhurries%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20her%20friends%20back%20home.%20It%20was%20time%20to%20leave.%20But%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321695%2Faamir-khanyari-turned-ancestral-land-into-traditional-kashmir-homestay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20rustic%20village%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20its%20mud%20homes%20and%20sprawling%20courtyards%20had%20cast%20a%20trance%20on%20her.%20She%20found%20it%20impossible%20to%20leave%20this%20vintage%20magic%20for%20the%20plushness%20of%20a%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Pukhraj%20ji%E2%80%99s%20son%20Chhotaram%20Prajapat%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20his%2030s%20recalls%2C%20the%20couple%20showed%20every%20intention%20to%20stay%20back%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20know%20English%20back%20then.%20But%20Brad%20and%20Lucy%20used%20sign%20language%20to%20ask%20us%20if%20they%20could%20live%20with%20us%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20We%20were%20surprised!%20Of%20course%20not!%E2%80%9D%20It%20was%20unheard%20of%20for%20foreigners%20to%20live%20with%20the%20villagers%20at%20the%20time.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20would%20we%20serve%20them%20to%20eat%3F%20Where%20would%20they%20sleep%3F%20All%20we%20could%20offer%20them%20was%20%3Cem%3Echarpais%20%3C%2Fem%3Eunder%20the%20open%20sky.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20compete%20with%20the%20luxuries%20of%20a%20hotel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Brad%20and%20Lucy%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ones%20to%20give%20up.%20The%20next%20morning%20they%20returned%20with%20a%20gentleman%20who%20was%20fluent%20in%20both%20English%20and%20Rajasthani%20dialect.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20communicated%20their%20request%20to%20us%20again%2C%20and%20told%20us%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20looking%20for%20luxuries%20but%20for%20an%20authentic%20Jodhpur%20experience%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290101%2Fbest-homestay-in-himachal-pradesh-sainj-valley-eco-friendly-kath-kuni-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20mud%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sleeping%20under%20the%20skies.%20Our%20home%20was%20perfect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20the%20couple%20were%20welcomed%20into%20Pukhraj%20ji%E2%80%99s%20home%20for%20the%20next%2015%20days.%20And%2C%20unknown%20to%20Chhotaram%2C%20this%20would%20set%20the%20precedent%20for%20his%20dream%20homestay%20business%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image