20and%20teaches%20guests%20to%20cook%20on%20an%20open%20fire%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chhotaram%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20the%20locals%20of%20the%20village%20of%20Salawas%20could%20be%20heard%20guiding%20many%20foreigners%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98mud%20home%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20was%20Chhotaram%E2%80%99s.%20Friends%20of%20Brad%20and%20Lucy%2C%20these%20people%20had%20heard%20of%20and%20seen%20pictures%20of%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20experience%20and%20were%20here%20to%20witness%20it%20for%20themselves.%20This%20time%2C%20Chhotaram%20was%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20oblige.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20hosted%20Brad%20and%20Lucy%20before%2C%20we%20were%20familiar%20with%20the%20spice%20that%20people%20abroad%20could%20tolerate%20and%20so%20we%20customised%20the%20food%20according%20to%20that.%E2%80%9D%20Meanwhile%2C%20Chhotaram%E2%80%99s%20English%20vocabulary%20had%20expanded%20and%20he%20was%20thoroughly%20enjoying%20his%20talks%20with%20the%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20conversation%20in%202011%20was%20the%20most%20significant%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20observed%20one%20of%20his%20guests%2C%20Brad%E2%80%99s%20friend%2C%20working%20on%20a%20laptop%20with%20a%20dongle%20for%20connectivity.%20He%E2%80%99d%20been%20staying%20with%20Chhotaram%20for%20three%20months%20at%20the%20time.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20talking%20and%20he%20suggested%20that%20I%20open%20up%20my%20home%20for%20tourism%20officially.%20Like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282723%2Fbest-homestays-in-ladakh-things-to-do-in-leh-local-experience%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20stranger%20to%20the%20internet%20and%20running%20a%20business%2C%20Chhotaram%20laughed%20it%20off.%20But%20the%20guest%20was%20persistent.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ll%20help%20you%20set%20it%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20promised.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20love%20your%20home%20over%20a%20hotel%20because%20of%20the%20local%20experience%20you%20give.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20at%20how%20this%20would%20work%2C%20Chotaram%20agreed.%20In%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%2C%20the%20guest%20had%20registered%20the%20home%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273684%2Fbest-ecofriendly-homestay-munnar-book-treehouse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravel%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20created%20an%20email%20address%20for%20Chhotaram%20through%20which%20he%20could%20access%20bookings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20was%20born%20the%20Chhotaram%20Prajapat%20Homestay.%20%E2%80%9CI%20came%20up%20with%20the%20name%20on%20the%20spur%20of%20the%20moment.%20I%20said%20%E2%80%98name%20it%20after%20me%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20paying%20Rs%20700%20to%20a%20local%20cyber%20cafe%20to%20access%20the%20internet%20for%20bookings%20and%20buying%20a%20computer%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20took%20two%20hours%20to%20reply%20to%20an%20email%E2%80%9D%20to%20now%20accepting%20bookings%20at%20the%20click%20of%20a%20button%2C%20Chhotaram%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20538px)%20100vw%2C%20538px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-13-at-6.30.23-AM-1707396796.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22538%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20food%20at%20the%20homestay%20includes%20Dal%20Bati%20Churma%2C%20which%20has%20masala%20bati%2C%20makki%20ki%20bati%2C%20and%20thirki%20dal%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-13-at-6.30.23-AM-1707396796.jpeg%20538w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-13-at-6.30.23-AM-1707396796-3